amount%20spent%20may%20be%20in%20excess%20of%20%2438.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Feconomics-hosting-olympic-games%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2018%20Winter%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Pyeongchang%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20cost%20about%20%2415%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Switzerland%20is%20already%20a%20winter%20sports%20hub%2C%20Swiss%20officials%20said%20they%20are%20aiming%20to%20keep%20costs%20down%20by%20using%20existing%20venues%20or%20refurbishing%20existing%20venues.%20They%20also%20said%20they%20would%20use%20existing%20accommodation%20rather%20than%20building%20a%20whole%20new%20games%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSwitzerland%20is%20lucky%20to%20already%20practically%20have%20all%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%2C%20ranging%20from%20sporting%20venues%20to%20its%20transport%20network%20and%20accommodation%2C%26quot%3B%20Urs%20Lehmann%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Swiss%20Ski%20Association%2C%20said%20last%20month%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fsports%2Fswitzerland-bid-2030-or-2034-winter-games-2023-11-24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BLet's%20seize%20this%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-switzerland-aims-host-cheapest-winter-olympics-budget-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701074702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564350dc58b6f84123a2c6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-switzerland-aims-host-cheapest-winter-olympics-budget-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Swiss%20Olympic%20Association%20said%20the%20country%20would%20be%20bidding%20for%20the%202030%20or%202034%20Winter%20Games.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%