india.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fgangs-extortion-in-bangladesh-camps-driving-rohingya-sea-exodus%2Famp_articleshow%2F105530865.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shamita%20Shetty%20thanks%20fans%20for%20responding%20to%20her%20Perimenopause%20post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701074380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105530712%2Cimgsize-994308.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fbigg-boss-15s-shamita-shetty-thanks-fans-for-responding-to-her-perimenopause-post-has-a-request-for-the-doctors-please-give-us-some-more-solutions-something-we-could-do-to-help-our-journey%2Farticleshow%2F105530445.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shamita%20Shetty%20thanked%20her%20Instagram%20followers%20for%20the%20response%20to%20her%20video%20on%20Perimenopause%20and%20for%20sharing%20their%20personal%20experiences%20and%20solutions.%20She%20acknowledged%20the%20doctors%20who%20responded%20and%20requested%20more%20solutions.%20Shamita%20also%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20the%20male%20followers%20who%20showed%20compassion.%20This%20interaction%20with%20her%20followers%20made%20her%20realize%20the%20importance%20of%20kindness%2C%20love%2C%20and%20care%20for%20each%20other.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20Shamita%20had%20to%20share%20about%20the%20discussion%2C%20solutions%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Clock%20Ticking%2C%20Rescuers%20Launch%20360%20Degree%20Op%20To%20Save%2041%20Trapped%20In%20Tunnel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20to%20rescue%2041%20workers%20trapped%20inside%20an%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20now%20has%20been%20a%20story%20of%20new%20challenges%20at%20every%20corner%20and%20rescue%20teams%20tweaking%20their%20plans%20to%20meet%20them.%20The%20past%2016%20days%20have%20seen%20government%20authorities%20constantly%20fine-tune%20their%20strategies%20and%20find%20new%20approaches%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20men%20at%20the%20earliest.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20rescue%20teams%20are%20drilling%20from%20multiple%20directions%20to%20reach%20the%20workers.%20They%20are%20simultaneously%20focusing%20on%20ensuring%20their%20physical%20and%20mental%20well-being%20as%20the%20operation%20drags%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20multiple%20plans%20in%20action%20now%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BAugering%20Is%20Finished%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20drilling%20at%20the%20Uttarkashi%20site%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20today%20after%20an%20auger%20drill%20machine%20manufactured%20in%20the%20US%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20debris.%20The%20drill%20--%20a%20corkscrew%20like-device%20with%20a%20rotary%20blade%20at%20the%20front-end%20--%20had%20drilled%20through%20more%20than%2046%20metres%20of%20debris.%20As%20the%20machine%20drilled%20through%2C%20pipes%20were%20pushed%20in%20to%20create%20an%20escape%20passage.%20A%20couple%20of%20days%20back%2C%20it%20appeared%20that%20the%20operation%20would%20be%20completed%20soon%2C%20but%20snags%20in%20the%20drill%20dashed%20hopes.%20About%2014-odd%20metres%20of%20drilling%20was%20left%20when%20the%20machine's%20blade%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20debris%20and%20the%20drill%20broke%20down.%20International%20tunnel%20expert%20Arnold%20Dix%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20site%2C%20said%20the%20auger%20machine%20was%20%26quot%3Bbusted%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAugering%20is%20finished...%20the%20auger%20is%20broken%2C%20destructed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%20Thereafter%2C%20a%20specialised%20gas%20cutter%20was%20flown%20in%20from%20Hyderabad%20to%20cut%20and%20remove%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20auger%20drill%20stuck%20in%20the%20debris%20so%20that%20manual%20drilling%20could%20begin.%20The%20plasma%20cutter%20completed%20its%20task%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManual%20Drilling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%2025-tonne%20auger%20machine%20breaking%20down%2C%20rescue%20teams%20decided%20to%20pursue%20multiple%20strategies%20simultaneously.%20Manual%20drilling%20is%20aimed%20at%20completing%20the%20task%20the%20auger%20drill%20started.%20A%20team%20of%2011%20has%20been%20flown%20in%20from%20Delhi%20for%20this%20task.%20These%20include%20six%20specialists%20and%20five%20more%20in%20reserve.%20Rescue%20teams%20said%20they%20will%20go%20inside%20the%20800%20mm%20pipe%20to%20remove%20the%20debris%20manually.%20This%20method%20involves%20two-three%20drillers%20entering%20the%20pipe%20and%20using%20hand-held%20tools%20to%20clear%20the%20debris%20blocking%20the%20pipe's%20way.%20The%20waste%20generated%20during%20the%20digging%20is%20sent%20out%20through%20wheeled%20vessels.%20One%20of%20the%20specialists%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%20%26quot%3BA%20shovel%20and%20other%20specialist%20tools%20will%20be%20used.%20For%20oxygen%2C%20we%20will%20take%20along%20a%20blower%20with%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20drilling%20is%20a%20tiring%20task%20and%20the%20diggers%20take%20turns.%20These%20professionals%20are%20also%20called%20rat%20miners%20for%20their%20rat-like%20skill%20in%20boring.%20According%20to%20rescue%20teams%2C%20these%20professionals%20are%20skilled%20in%20cutting%20through%20metal%20barriers%20too.%20Manual%20drilling%20method%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20today.%20Rescue%20teams%20at%20the%20site%20said%20this%20morning%20that%20the%20gas%20cutters%20used%20to%20remove%20parts%20of%20the%20auger%20drill%20from%20the%20debris%20had%20generated%20heat%20inside%20the%20pipe%20and%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20it%20to%20cool%20down%20before%20manual%20drilling%20starts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVertical%20Drilling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20horizontal%20drilling%20operation%20facing%20repeated%20hurdles%2C%20rescue%20teams%20have%20put%20in%20action%20a%20vertical%20drilling%20plan.%20This%20plan%20involves%20drilling%20horizontally%20from%20a%20point%20about%20300%20metres%20from%20the%20mouth%20of%20the%20tunnel%20and%20then%20drilling%20vertically%20down%20about%2086%20metres.%20Former%20chief%20of%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20Harpal%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20site%2C%20has%20said%2031%20metres%20of%20drilling%20has%20been%20completed.%20A%20big%20challenge%20in%20the%20vertical%20drilling%20method%20is%20how%20to%20drill%20through%20the%20crust%20or%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20Rescue%20teams%20plan%20to%20drill%20horizontally%20for%20a%20short%20distance%20once%20they%20reach%20the%20crust%2C%20and%20then%20drill%20through%20it%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20workers%20trapped%20beneath%20it%20are%20not%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vertical%20drilling%20method%20was%20put%20into%20action%20yesterday%20by%20Satluj%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%2C%20a%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20involved%20in%20hydroelectric%20power%20generation.%20This%20method%20has%20progressed%20smoothly%20so%20far.%20The%20team%20drilling%20through%20the%20mountain%20plans%20to%20pull%20up%20the%2041%20labourers%20using%20a%20harness%20machine%20once%20it%20reaches%20them.%20According%20to%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%2C%20the%20drilling%20work%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Other%20Methods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20teams%20have%20also%20started%20an%20operation%20to%20reach%20the%20trapped%20workers%20through%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20from%20Barkot.%20But%20that%20is%20a%20method%20that%20is%20going%20to%20take%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20rescuers%20have%20to%20drill%20through%20nearly%20480%20metres.%20Four%20blasts%20were%20carried%20out%20yesterday%20to%20help%20them%20progress.%20Only%2010%20metres%20have%20been%20covered%20so%20far.%20There%20is%20another%20plan%20that%20involves%20building%20a%20mini%20tunnel%20along%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20This%20mini%20tunnel%20will%20be%20perpendicular%20to%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%2C%20and%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20rescue%20the%20trapped%20workers%20through%20it.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20this%20perpendicular%20mini%20tunnel%20will%20be%20180%20metres%20long%2C%20and%20it%20will%20take%20another%2010%20to%2015%20days%20to%20be%20built.%20Work%20on%20this%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Are%20The%20Workers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rescue%20operation%20drags%20on%2C%20there%20is%20concern%20over%20the%20mental%20and%20physical%20condition%20of%20the%20workers.%20While%20they%20are%20now%20receiving%20food%20and%20other%20essential%20supplies%20through%20a%20pipe%20pushed%20through%20the%20debris%2C%20their%20mental%20state%20remains%20a%20cause%20for%20worry.%20Over%20the%20past%2016%20days%2C%20they%20have%20gone%20through%20the%20trauma%20of%20being%20stuck%20inside%20a%20tunnel%2C%20the%20fear%20that%20help%20may%20not%20reach%20them%2C%20some%20moments%20of%20hope%20when%20it%20appeared%20that%20they%20will%20soon%20be%20out%20and%20a%20return%20to%20uncertainty%20on%20when%20they%20will%20see%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20Rescue%20teams%20are%20aware%20that%20the%20mental%20state%20of%20the%20workers%20will%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20keeping%20them%20fine%20till%20the%20end%20of%20this%20long-drawn%20operation.%20They%20have%20now%20roped%20Bharat%20Sanchar%20Nigam%20Limited%20to%20provide%20the%20trapped%20workers%20with%20a%20landline%20connection%20so%20that%20they%20can%20talk%20to%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBSNL%20official%20Kundan%20said%20they%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20sending%20a%20small%20landline%20phone%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers%20through%20the%20pipe.%20%26quot%3BThrough%20this%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20talk%20directly%20to%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%20BSNL%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20set%20up%20a%20small%20telephone%20exchange%20at%20the%20tunnel%20site%20for%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20mobile%20phones%20have%20also%20been%20sent%20through%20the%20pipe%20so%20that%20the%20trapped%20workers%20can%20play%20video%20games%20to%20distract%20themselves%20from%20the%20harrowing%20wait%20to%20be%20rescued.%20Rescue%20teams%20said%20there%20are%20plans%20to%20provide%20Wi-Fi%20connectivity%20because%20there%20is%20no%20cellphone%20network%20inside%20the%20tunnel.%20Board%20games%20have%20also%20been%20sent%20through%20the%20pipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Weather%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-freezing-temperatures-rain-pose-fresh-challenge-to-uttarakhand-rescue-op-4609401%5C%22%3EWeather%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20predicted%20light%20rain%20at%20the%20tunnel%20rescue%20site%20this%20evening.%20The%20temperature%20at%20the%20site%20has%20also%20dropped%20to%20as%20low%20as%204%20degrees%20Celsius.%20While%20this%20could%20create%20complications%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%20the%20teams%20working%20on%20the%20ground%20said%20they%20are%20prepared%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20challenge.%20A%20report%20in%20Reuters%20quoted%20Mahmood%20Ahmad%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20NHIDCL%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20rescue%20workers%20are%20%26quot%3Btrained%20in%20working%20in%20every%20situation%2C%20so%20that's%20not%20a%20worry%20for%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701074040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhaoge2u8_uttarkashi-tunnel_625x300_27_November_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-rescue-uttarkashi-tunnel-silkyara-manual-to-vertical-