E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfakes%20of%20several%20celebrities%20-%20including%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%2C%20Kajol%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20Sara%20Tendulkar%20-%20had%20earlier%20surfaced%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20sparking%20concerns%20over%20the%20misuse%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20video%20shows%20a%20woman%20with%20the%20morphed%20face%20of%20Alia%20Bhatt%20making%20obscene%20gestures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20have%20sparked%20massive%20worry%20about%20fake%20videos%20targeting%20public%20figures%20and%20the%20power%20of%20AI%20to%20create%20deepfakes%20that%20can%20mislead%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20said%20that%20the%20creation%20and%20circulation%20of%20deepfakes%20carry%20a%20strong%20penalty%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20fine%20and%20three%20years%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20last%20week%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20will%20soon%20appoint%20an%20officer%20to%20take%20appropriate%20action%20against%20such%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20that%20the%20existing%20laws%20and%20Rules%20have%20clear%20provisions%20to%20deal%20with%20Deepfake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(Meity)%20will%20develop%20a%20website%20on%20which%20users%20can%20flag%20their%20concerns%20about%20IT%20rule%20violation.%20%26quot%3BMeity%20will%20assist%20users%20to%20notify%20it%20about%20violation%20of%20IT%20rules%20and%20assist%20them%20in%20filing%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20or%20FIR%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20also%20flagged%20the%20misuse%20of%20AI%20for%20creating%20deepfake%20videos%20and%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20concern.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20times%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that