e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27125235%2F400885315_926965215455506_1904449686751089128_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Sunday%20asked%20officials%20to%20conduct%20a%20door-to-door%20survey%20to%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20alcohol%20prohibition%2C%20imposed%20by%20his%20government%20seven%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fbihar%2Fstory%2Fnitish-calls-for-fresh-survey-to-study-impact-of-prohibition-in-bihar-2467868-2023-11-27%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kumar%20made%20these%20remarks%20at%20an%20event%20on%20%E2%80%98Nashamukti%20Diwas%E2%80%99%20(Deaddiction%20Day)%2C%20which%20is%20observed%20every%20November%2026.%20Bihar%20imposed%20total%20prohibition%20in%20April%202016%2C%20banning%20the%20manufacture%2C%20trade%2C%20storage%2C%20possession%20and%20consumption%20of%20all%20types%20of%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fbihar-chief-minister-nitish-kumar-asks-officials-to-conduct-a-door-to-door-survey-on-prohibition-impact%2Fcid%2F1982803%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kumar%20said%20that%20a%20survey%20conducted%20in%202018%20to%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20prohibition%20revealed%20that%20%E2%80%9C1.64%20crore%20people%20in%20the%20state%20quit%20drinking%2C%20while%20another%20done%20in%202023%20brought%20to%20light%20that%201.82%20crore%20people%20have%20stopped%20consuming%20liquor%E2%80%9D.%20It%20showed%20that%2099%25%20of%20women%20and%2092%25%20of%20men%20in%20Bihar%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20prohibition%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20survey%2C%20the%20loss%20in%20revenue%20was%20more%20than%20offset%20by%20the%20money%20people%20were%20saving%20and%20spending%20on%20improving%20their%20economic%20condition%20and%20ensuring%20better%20education%20for%20their%20children.%20Besides%2C%20there%20are%20studies%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20which%20enlist%20harmful%20effects%20of%20alcohol%20consumption%2C%20including%20fatal%20road%20accidents%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20ban%20would%20not%20be%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20urge%20the%20people%20here%20to%20consider%20a%20fresh%20survey%20which%20would%20give%20a%20fresh%20estimate%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20prohibition.%20Based%20on%20the%20findings%2C%20we%20would%20introduce%20fresh%20measures.%20But%20I%20must%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20prohibition%20is%20there%20to%20stay%2C%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20am%20in%20charge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701070171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27125235%2F400885315_926965215455506_1904449686751089128_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbihar-nitish-kumar-survey-impact-prohibition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20loss%20in%20revenue%20due%20to%20the%20liquor%20ban%20was%20more%20than%20offset%20by%20the%20money%20people%20were%20saving%20and%20spending%20on%20improving%20their%20economic%20condition%20and%20ensuring%20better%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbihar-nitish-kumar-survey-impact-prohibition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dental%20student%20jumps%20from%2022-storey%20bldg%20in%20NCR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701070096000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105529251%2Cimgsize-1087975.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fghaziabad%2Fdental-college-student-jumps-from-terrace-of-22-store