%20not%20a%20worry%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahmood%20Ahmed%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20NHIDCL%20company%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-in-tunnel-op-manual-drilling-likely-today-after-parts-of-machine-removed-4608823%5C%22%3EIn%20Uttarkashi%20Tunnel%20Op%2C%20Manual%20Drilling%20Today%20As%20Broken%20Drill%20Removed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrapped%20in%20the%20tunnel%20for%20over%20360%20hours%20and%20nearly%2016%20days%2C%20the%2041%20workers%20may%20face%20an%20extended%20wait%20for%20their%20rescue%2C%20possibly%20stretching%20by%20days%20or%20even%20weeks%2C%20before%20their%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers'%20prolonged%20confinement%20within%20the%20tunnel%20is%20raising%20serious%20concerns%20about%20their%20health%20and%20well-being.%20Doctors%20have%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20rehabilitation%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20prolonged%20confinement%20may%20necessitate%20both%20mental%20and%20physical%20recovery%20processes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ahmed%20said%20the%20vertical%20drilling%20process%2C%20which%20commenced%20yesterday%2C%20will%20be%20successfully%20concluded%20by%20Thursday%2C%20provided%20no%20unforeseen%20obstacles%20arise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-rescue-manual-digging-specialist-details-operation-to-remove-debris-4609244%5C%22%3EUttarkashi%20Tunnel%20Rescue%3A%20Manual%20Digging%20Specialist%20Details%20Op%20To%20Remove%20Debris%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlades%20of%20the%20damaged%20auger%20drill%20have%20been%20extracted%20from%20the%20tunnel.%20The%20auger%20drill%2C%20a%20corkscrew-shaped%20device%20with%20a%20rotating%20blade%20at%20the%20tip%2C%20became%20stuck%20in%20the%20debris.%20This%20forced%20officials%20to%20abandon%20the%2025-tonne%20machine%2C%20which%20had%20been%20making%20progress%20in%20the%20excavation%20process.%20Manual%20drilling%20will%20now%20commence%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20an%20escape%20route%2C%20offering%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20to%20the%2041%20stranded%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicro%20tunneling%20expert%20Chris%20Cooper%20said%20today%20that%20the%20debris%20from%20the%20auger%20machine%20has%20been%20cleared%20and%20manual%20drilling%20will%20begin%20in%20a%20few%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20debris%20(of%20the%20Auger%20machine)%20removed.%20(Manual%20drilling)%20will%20probably%20start%20after%203%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Cooper%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%209%20meters%20of%20hand%20tunnelling%20to%20do.%20It%20really%20depends%20on%20how%20the%20ground%20behaves.%20Could%20be%20quickly%2C%20could%20be%20a%20bit%20longer.%20If%20we%20hit%20some%20lattice%20girder.%20Then%20we've%20got%20to%20cut%20out%20the%20lattice%20girder%2C%20but%20we're%20confident%20we%20can%20get%20through.%20The%20Army%20is%20just%20supervising%20(the%20operation).%2030%20metres%20of%20(vertical%20drilling)%20has%20been%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%2010-15%20metres%20will%20now%20have%20to%20be%20broken%20with%20hand-held%20power%20tools%2C%20a%20significantly%20more%20time-consuming%20process.%20Workers%20are%20entering%20the%20unfinished%20escape%20passage%2C%20equipped%20with%20a%20steel%20chute%2C%20to%20dismantle%20the%20jammed%20auger%20blades%20and%20shaft.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701070080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F81f11hu8_uttarakhand-tunnel-reuters-_625x300_27_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-freezing-temperatures-rain-pose-fresh-challenge-to-uttarakhand-rescue-op-460940