ltural%20cliches%2C%20a%20few%20lazy%20stereotypes%2C%20and%20a%20very%20peculiar%20human%20need%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20an%20outcome%20that%E2%80%99s%20mostly%20the%20result%20of%20a%20completely%20random%20set%20of%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mythologising%20involves%20a%20fundamentally%20incorrect%20understanding%20of%20how%20a%20sporting%20contest%20between%20roughly%20equal%20opponents%20works.%20It%20assumes%20a%20given%20outcome%20is%20the%20result%20of%20something%20deeper%20than%20what%E2%80%99s%20apparent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20level%20of%20emotional%20attachment%20fans%20follow%20a%20contest%20with%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20somewhat%20hard%20to%20stomach%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20result%20is%20entirely%20determined%20by%20events%20on%20the%20field%3B%20and%20that%20the%20slightest%20change%20in%20some%20in-game%20variables%20could%E2%80%99ve%20forced%20an%20opposite%20outcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20inherent%20limitation%20of%20outcome-oriented%20analysis.%20It%20fails%20to%20both%20account%20for%20and%20adequately%20understand%20the%20principle%20of%20randomness%20%E2%80%93%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20determinant%20of%20margins%20within%20which%20a%20match%20is%20won%20or%20lost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20sport%20in%20modern%20times%20is%20mostly%20consumed%20on%20television%20and%20the%20medium%20requires%20it%20to%20be%20presented%20with%20a%20certain%20tonality%20for%20effect%2C%20the%20audience%20has%20grown%20increasingly%20desperate%20to%20find%20explanations%20for%20a%20team%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20meaningless%20intangibles.%20Tags%20like%20%E2%80%98serial%20winners%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98chokers%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98stepping-up-when-it-matters%E2%80%99%20are%20thrown%20about%20loosely%20and%20television%20commentary%20that%20assists%20a%20fan%E2%80%99s%20viewing%20experience%20does%20everything%20in%20its%20power%20to%20solidify%20these%20notions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20tendency%20is%20prevalent%20across%20all%20major%20sports%2C%20cricket%20perhaps%20takes%20the%20crown%20for%20allowing%20these%20empty%20labels%20to%20completely%20hijack%20the%20discourse.%20The%20Australians%2C%20in%20this%20universe%20of%20fanciful%20imaginations%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%20the%20genetic%20code%20to%20win%20tournaments%20with%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcricketworldcup%2Fstatus%2F1726758248299061491%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewinners%E2%80%99%20DNA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewhile%20India%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20are%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fsports%2Fworld-cup-chokers-india-searches-for-answers-after-latest-letdown%2Farticleshow%2F105350361.cms%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eperennial%20chokers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20now%2C%20having%20upstaged%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%93%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcricket%2Fworld-cup%2Fcurse-of-the-knockouts-south-africa-s-choking-history-at-the-world-cups-123111600193_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eheld%20on%20to%20this%20(dubious)%20title%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20television%20age.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20World%20Cup%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20where%20Australia%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecomprehensively%20beat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20India%20in%20front%20of%20a%20jampacked%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%2C%20reignited%20this%20discourse%20again.%20The%20final%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20culmination%20point%20of%20the%20perfect%20Indian%20dream.%20The%20team%20had%20entered%20the%20final%20as%20firm%20favourites%2C%20having%20won%20ten%20games%20on%20the%20bounce.%20Australia%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20had%20started%20slow%2C%20struggled%20to%20find%20their%20best%20combination%20and%20almost%20made%20a%20mess%20of%20what%20should%E2%80%99ve%20been%20a%20straightforward%20chase%20in%20the%20semifinal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20ten-match%20winning%20streak%2C%20India%20encountered%20every%20possible%20game%20scenario%20and%20came%20out%20unscathed.%20Their%20bowlers%20constantly%20restricted%20teams%20to%20below-par%20totals%20when%20bowling%20first%20on%20slow%20tracks%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20batting%20teams%20out%20of%20the%20contest%20on%20flat%20pitches%20was%20no%20trouble%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESkipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20batted%20with%20unmatched%20flair%20and%20put%20the%20team%20in%20a%20position%20of%20dominance%20game%20after%20game.%20Virat%20Kohli%20cracked%20the%20perfect%20pace%20for%20the%20middle%20order%20to%20bat%20around%20him%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20innings.%20And%20few%20had%20answers%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20fast-bowling%20menace%20of%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami.%20What%20exactly%20was%20there%20to%20stop%20the%20Indian%20juggernaut%20other%20than%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebig%20game%20pressure%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Efear%20of%20failure%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eburden%20of%20expectations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-mata-ki-jai-jingoism-lost-in-ahmedabad-on-sunday%5C%22%3ECricket%20Mata%20Ki%20Jai%3A%20Jingoism%20Lost%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadly%2C%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20game%20of%20cricket%20for%20the%20most%20part%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20too%20much%20to%20do%20with%20any%20of%20the%20above%20and%20instead%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20too%20much%20to%20do%20with%20that%2022-yard%20strip%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20ground.%20On%20a%20sluggish%20surface%20where%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20trust%20the%20pace%20and%20bounce%20of%20the%20ball%2C%20India%20were%20at%20a%20considerable%20disadvantage%20having%20to%20bat%20first%20after%20losing%20the%20toss.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarring%20Sharma%20and%20to%20an%20extent%20Kohli%2C%20every%20Indian%20batsman%20struggled%20to%20time%20the%20ball%20and%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20meticulously%20planned%20bowling%20tactics%20didn%E2%80%99t%20help%20much%20either.%20Sure%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20final%20did%20play%20its%20part%3B%20in%20that%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20imagine%20India%20scoring%20all%20of%20four%20boundaries%20over%20a%2040-over%20stretch%20on%20a%20lesser%20occasion%20with%20their%20legacies%20not%20being%20written%20about%20in%20real-time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20fair%20to%20assume%20the%20Indian%20middle%20order%20may%20perhaps%20have%20taken%20a%20few%20more%20risks%20and%20pushed%20the%20score%20more%20than%20they%20did%20were%20it%20not%20for%20the%20hype%20around%20what%20was%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20match%20of%20their%20careers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20two%20part-timers%20(Mitchell%20Marsh%20and%20Travis%20Head)%20getting%20away%20with%20four%20overs%20between%20them%20conceding%20only%20nine%20on%20any%20other%20day.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20only%20so%20much%20these%20psychological%20factors%20influence%20the%20course%20of%20a%20game%20between%20two%20high-quality%20teams.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20indeed%20was%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20playing%20conditions%20in%20the%20final%20from%20the%20earlier%20stages%20of%20the%20tournament%20that%20completely%20stagnated%20India%E2%80%99s%20scoring%20rate%20and%20kept%20them%20well%20short%20of%20what%20would%E2%80%99ve%20been%20a%20challenging%20total.%20Having%20to%20chase%20a%20modest%20score%20by%20modern%20standards%20and%20batting%20on%20a%20fairly%20settled%20pitch%20under%20lights%2C%20Australia%20made%20light%20work%20of%20the%20target.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Australian%20bowlers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fluster%20despite%20the%20early%20onslaught%20by%20India%20and%20stuck%20to%20their%20plan%20of%20denying%20the%20batters%20any%20pace%20on%20the%20ball%20by%20constantly%20bowling%20into%20the%20pitch.%20Captain%20Pat%20Cummins%20in%20particular%20had%20a%20day%20he%20will%20never%20tire%20of%20talking%20about%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life.%20But%20to%20ignore%20the%20competitive%20advantage%20he%20gained%20at%20the%20toss%20on%20that%20day%20would%20be%20a%20dishonest%20appraisal%20of%20his%20effort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chase%20was%20even%20funnier.%20The%20entire%20top%20order%20came%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20throw%20their%20hands%20against%20anything%20remotely%20wide%20while%20the%20ball%20was%20hard%20and%20came%20decently%20onto%20the%20bat.%20David%20Warner%20and%20Mitchell%20Marsh%20perished%20to%20this%20philosophy%20while%20Travis%20Head%20managed%20to%20survive%20despite%20no%20discernibly%20different%20technique%20and%20lived%20to%20tell%20the%20tale%20of%20his%20heroics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESure%2C%20Head%20went%20on%20to%20ruthlessly%20dominate%20the%20Indian%20bowling%20once%20the%20ball%20stopped%20moving%20as%20viciously%20but%20his%20survival%20to%20that%20point%20involved%20an%20insane%20amount%20of%20luck%20%E2%80%93%20not%20some%20mentality%20potion%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Estand%20up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhen%20it%20counts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Australians%20have%20secretly%20gotten%20hold%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20clear%20and%20coherent%20cricketing%20explanation%20that%20highlights%20the%20difference%20in%20how%20the%20two%20teams%20performed%20in%20the%20final.%20But%20to%20attribute%20the%20result%20entirely%20to%20a%20fairly%20unintelligent%20and%20rudimentary%20understanding%20of%20cultures%20is%20laughably%20reductive.%20The%20cricket%20media%20and%20commentary%20teams%2C%20however%2C%20wholeheartedly%20indulge%20in%20this%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH-300x158.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH-1024x540.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685550%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%20celebrates%20after%20winning%20the%202023%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40cricketworldcup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeak%20narratives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20punditry%20today%20borrows%20their%20perceptions%20of%20Australia%20from%20the%20indomitable%20team%20under%20Steve%20Waugh%20and%20Ricky%20Ponting%20that%20bagged%20three%20World%20Cup%20titles%20on%20the%20trot.%20While%20the%20aura%20of%20that%20team%20indeed%20was%20extremely%20intimidating%2C%20the%20dominance%20was%20simply%20down%20to%20them%20being%20remarkably%20better%20than%20everyone%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20conceded%20that%20cricketing%20prepotency%20lent%20them%20some%20mental%20edge%20over%20opponents%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20fatuous%20to%20assume%20that%20mentality%20transcends%20across%20eras%20and%20that%20an%20Australian%20team%20today%20%E2%80%93%20with%20no%20trace%20whatsoever%20to%20that%20one%20%E2%80%93%20continues%20to%20be%20of%20similar%20mental%20makeup.%20The%20implication%20is%20insincere%20and%20borders%20on%20a%20belief%20in%20racial%20supremacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20narrative%20formed%20around%20the%20current%20Indian%20team%20is%20on%20equally%20thin%20grounds.%20That%20India%20has%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20relevant%20trophy%20in%20limited-overs%20tournaments%20for%20ten%20years%20now%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20handle%20pressure%20in%20high-profile%20knockout%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20End%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20Always%20XI%20Versus%20XI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20very%20cursory%20glance%20at%20these%20handful%20of%20games%20would%20reveal%20India%20got%20outclassed%20at%20least%20twice%20by%20decisively%20better%20oppositions%20(Australia%20in%20the%202015%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20and%20England%20in%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup).%20In%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20conditions%20suited%20New%20Zealand%E2%80%99s%20seam%20bowling%20perfectly%2C%20whereas%20India%20paid%20a%20heavy%20price%20for%20losing%20the%20toss%20in%20their%20defeats%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20West%20Indies%20in%20the%202014%20and%202016%20T20%20World%20Cups%20respectively.%20The%202017%20Champions%20Trophy%20thrashing%20to%20Pakistan%20is%20the%20only%20one%20hard%20to%20explain%20in%20plain%20cricketspeak%20but%20that%20it%20was%20an%20anomaly%20is%20sufficiently%20proved%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20of%20Pakistan%20in%20ODIs%20on%20either%20side%20of%20that%20game.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final%20defeats%20are%20now%20added%20to%20the%20list%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20glorious%20big-stage%20failures.%20This%20argument%20perhaps%20stands%20on%20the%20weakest%20legs%2C%20not%20that%20the%20others%20are%20particularly%20sound.%20The%20WTC%20final%20is%20a%20one-off%20exhibition%20Test%20match%20played%20in%20conditions%20where%20India%20starts%20at%20a%20massive%20disadvantage%20against%20the%20teams%20it%E2%80%99s%20realistically%20likely%20to%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20Indian%20Test%20team%E2%80%99s%20two%20series%20wins%20in%20Australia%20are%20a%20far%20bigger%20accomplishment%20than%20a%20WTC%20title%2C%20literally%20invented%20to%20infuse%20artificial%20excitement%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20Winning%20a%20single%20Test%20in%20Australia%20is%20objectively%20harder%20than%20qualifying%20for%20and%20winning%20the%20Test%20championship.%20For%20India%20to%20have%20won%20a%20series%20and%20repeat%20that%20again%20is%20a%20generational%20achievement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20this%20is%20to%20suggest%20fans%20should%20have%20no%20qualms%20over%20India%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20silverware.%20But%20to%20imply%20they%20lack%20the%20bottle%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20proverbial%20big%20day%20is%20both%20amateurish%20and%20lacks%20a%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20sport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECertainly%2C%20players%20experience%20greater%20pressure%20to%20perform%20on%20big%20occasions.%20This%20may%20show%20up%20in%20a%20more%20guarded%20and%20tentative%20approach%20they%20take.%20Batsmen%20may%20carry%20more%20self-doubt%20to%20execute%20some%20risky%20shots.%20But%20much%20like%20most%20games%20of%20cricket%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebig%20ones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20too%20swing%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other%20based%20on%20the%20same%20set%20of%20variables%20%E2%80%93%20pitch%2C%20conditions%2C%20toss%2C%20and%20some%20happenstance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20nothing%20about%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20game%20that%20explained%20the%20returns%20of%209%2C%201%2C%20and%201%20in%20the%20three%20World%20Cup%20semifinals%20he%E2%80%99d%20played%20before%20the%202023%20edition.%20And%20even%20a%20magnificent%20hundred%20in%20his%20fourth%20attempt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20guarantee%20he%20could%20be%20dismissed%20cheaply%20in%20the%20next%20one%20%E2%80%93%20should%20he%20make%20it%20that%20far%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701069646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27121214%2FF_NTX9lbYAAsGNV-1080x600-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-notions-winning-dna-choking-gene-world-cup%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20big%20games%20too%20swing%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other%20based%20on%20the%20same%20set%20of%20variables%20%E2%80%93%20pitch%2C%20conditions%2C%20toss%2C%20and%20some%20happenstance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-notions-winning-dna-choking-gene-world-cup%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beijing%20frets%20over%20Taiwan%20opposition%20split%20as%20parties%20go%20on%20the%20attack%20over%20China%20ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701069610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105529043%2Cimgsize-44664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-frets-over-taiwan-opposition-split-as-parties-go-on-the-attack-over-china-ties%2Farticleshow%2F105529007.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22htt