%9CI%20thought%20caste%20discrimination%20does%20not%20exist%20here.%20I%20was%20very%20depressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pariyar%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20a%20family%20in%20the%20Hindu%20Dalit%20caste%2C%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20discriminatorily%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CUntouchables%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0is%20one%20of%20many%20South%20Asian%20advocates%20pushing%20forward%20efforts%20to%20legally%20recognize%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Funited-states-of-america%2Ft-19065189%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20caste%20is%20commonly%20referred%20to%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20India%2C%20it%20is%20a%20social%20hierarchy%20system%20that%20is%20thousands%20of%20years%20old%20and%20recognized%20in%20several%20countries%20across%20the%20region%2C%20including%20Nepal%2C%20where%20Pariyar%20grew%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20educate%20everyone%20so%20that%20this%20system%20will%20be%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20isolated%20generation%20to%20generation.%20There%20is%20intergenerational%20trauma.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20discrimination%20crossing%20borders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%20decided%20to%20come%20to%20the%20US%20after%20his%20family%20was%20violently%20attacked%20because%20of%20their%20caste%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20in%20their%20home%20in%20the%20Nepalese%C2%A0capital%2C%20Kathmandu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20tried%20to%20file%20charges%20against%20the%20assailant%2C%20the%20authorities%20did%20nothing%2C%20and%20even%20threatened%20him%20for%20taking%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%C2%A0proceeded%20to%20find%20a%20job%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20his%20employer%20offered%20to%20house%20him.%20However%2C%20his%20colleagues%20in%20the%20house%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20share%20a%20room%20with%20him%2C%20making%20casteist%20claims%20and%20slurs.%20So%2C%20he%20slept%20on%20the%20couch%C2%A0instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPariyar%2C%20who%20is%20now%20on%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20for%20the%20California%20chapter%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Social%20Workers%2C%20said%20his%20story%20is%20not%20unique.%20While%20he%20had%20hoped%20to%20leave%20this%20form%20of%20discrimination%20behind%20in%20Nepal%2C%20he%20said%20he%20and%20several%20others%20have%20faced%20significant%20hurdles%20in%20employment%20and%20even%20safety%20upon%20coming%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20over%205.4%20million%20South%20Asians%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20concentrated%20in%20California.%20They%20are%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20growing%20demographic%20groups%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20many%20people%20coming%20to%20work%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20in%20California%E2%80%99s%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20US-based%20Dalits%20have%20said%20the%20system%20of%20discrimination%20has%20followed%20them%2C%20resulting%20in%20harassment%2C%20sabotage%20in%20the%20workplace%20and%20even%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20activists%20have%20united%20under%20new%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Californians%20for%20Caste%20Equity%20Coalition%20and%20Equality%20Labs%2C%C2%A0both%20instrumental%20in%20the%20push%20for%20legal%20recognitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20setback%20after%20California%20vetoes%20bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20following%20over%20a%20year%20of%20advocacy%20and%20a%20monthlong%20hunger%20strike%20by%20supporters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcalifornia-governor-scraps-bill-against-caste-discrimination%2Fa-67030645%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20vetoed%20Senate%20Bill%20403%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20have%20made%20the%20state%20the%20first%20to%20include%20caste%20in%20the%20list%20of%20protected%20classes%20under%20civil%20rights%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20would%20have%20offered%20employment%20and%20housing%20protections%20alongside%20categories%20such%20as%20race%2C%20gender%20and%20sexual%20orientation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20(31-5%20in%20the%20Senate)%2C%20Newsom%20called%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%9Cunnecessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20saying%20that%20protections%20against%C2%A0caste-based%C2%A0discrimination%C2%A0are%20covered%20legally%20under%20already%20existing%20protections%20that%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20be%20liberally%20construed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veto%20created%20an%20uproar%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20community%2C%20spurring%20rallies%20at%20the%20capitol%2C%20lobbying%20lines%20through%20hallways%2C%20and%20a%C2%A0hunger%20strike%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20opposing%20the%20bill%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Hindu%20American%20Foundation%2C%20called%20it%C2%A0both%20racist%20and%20a%20potential%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutional%20disaster%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20would%20have%20%E2%80%9Cput%20a%20target%20on%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Californians%20simply%20because%20of%20their%20ethnicity%20or%20racial%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20Newsom%E2%80%99s%20veto%20decision%20have%20said%20he%20made%20the%20move%C2%A0in%20order%20to%20maintain%20relations%20with%20a%20growing%20Hindu%20voting%20base%2C%20which%20largely%20upholds%20the%20caste%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20process%2C%20we%20shined%20a%20light%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcaste-in-the-us-california-lawmakers-try-to-tackle-discrimination%2Fa-65355964%5C%22%3Elong-hidden%20form%20of%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20persists%20across%20multiple%20communities%20in%20California%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Senator%20Aisha%20Wahab%2C%20the%20first%20Muslim%20and%20Afghan%20American%20woman%20elected%20to%20the%20state%20legislature%2C%20and%20the%20author%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEfforts%20pick%20up%20steam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20veto%2C%20Fresno%2C%20a%20city%20in%20California%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Valley%2C%20unanimously%20agreed%20to%20ban%20caste-based%20discrimination%20specifically%C2%A0about%20a%20week%20prior%20to%20the%20veto%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Seattle%20became%20the%20first%20US%20city%20to%20outlaw%20caste-based%20discrimination.%20Educational%20institutions%2C%20including%20California%20State%20University%2C%20Harvard%2C%20Brandeis%20and%20the%20University%20of%20California%20%E2%80%93%20Davis%2C%20have%20all%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20made%20separate%20legal%20provisions%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20corporate%20world%20has%20also%20added%20to%20the%20movement%2C%20with%20tech%20giants%20including%20Apple%20and%20IBM%20updating%20employee%20policies%20to%20include%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20protections%20follow%20a%202020%20lawsuit%20initiated%20by%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Fair%20Employment%20and%20Housing%20against%20Cisco%2C%20a%20%24195%20billion%20(%E2%82%AC178%20billion)%20company%2C%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20a%20Dalit%20employee%20had%20been%20severely%20discriminated%20against%20by%20supervisors%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Chigher%E2%80%9D%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20caste%20discrimination%20been%20recognized%20then%2C%20advocates%20have%20said%2C%20the%20employee%20could%20have%20won%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Pariyar%20said%20recent%20legal%20efforts%20have%20united%20the%20Dalit%20community%20and%20others%20fighting%20for%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20more%20cities%20are%20rethinking%20caste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20I%20was%20alone.%20Now%2C%20our%20pe