%20convey.%20Additionally%2C%20men%20and%20women%20are%20not%20equal.%20The%20day%20men%20start%20getting%20pregnant%2C%20that%20day%20we%20will%20be%20equal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeena%20Gupta%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20men%20in%20women's%20lives.%20Sharing%20her%20own%20experience%2C%20the%20actress%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20a%20man.%20I%20will%20tell%20a%20small%20story.%20I%20had%20to%20catch%20a%20flight%20at%206%20am.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20boyfriend%20at%20that%20time.%20I%20came%20out%20of%20the%20house%20at%204%20am%20and%20it%20was%20dark.%20A%20man%20started%20following%20me%2C%20and%20I%20was%20so%20scared.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20my%20house%20and%20I%20missed%20my%20flight.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20I%20booked%20the%20same%20flight.%20But%20I%20stayed%20at%20my%20male%20friend's%20house%20and%20he%20dropped%20me%20off.%20I%20need%20a%20man.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeena%20Gupta's%20comment%20on%20feminism%20has%20everyone%20talking.%20Replying%20to%20the%20clip%20shared%20on%20Instagram%2C%20actress%20Tannaz%20Irani%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20one%20woman%20who%20has%20had%20the%20guts%20to%20live%20her%20life%20on%20her%20own%20terms.%20Don't%20regret%20anything%20you%20have%20ever%20done.%20It's%20made%20you%20the%20wonderful%20person%20you%20are%20today.%20And%20your%20daughter%20should%20and%20she%20is%20so%20proud%20of%20you%20too!%20I'm%20sure.%E2%80%9D%20Actress%20Sunita%20Rajwar%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CLove%20and%20respect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFans%20have%20given%20a%20shout-out%20to%20the%20actress%20for%20her%20%E2%80%9Ccourage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20lived%20life%20to%20the%20fullest.%20Learned%20lessons%20along%20the%20way.%20That's%20called%20life.%20So%20proud%20of%20her%2C%20so%20happy%20for%20her.%20She%20really%20lived%20a%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrue...male%20and%20female%20can't%20be%20equal%20in%20everything%E2%80%A6God%20has%20made%20them%20different.%20Together%20they%20can%20be%2050-50%20partners%20overall.%20But%20not%20be%2050-50%20in%20every%20single%20matter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20honest%20female%20celebrity%20ever..%20she%20says%20what%20she%20believes%20in%20as%20it%20is.%20No%20trying%20to%20give%20a%20politically%20correct%20answer.%20Love%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20a%20fan%20on%20YouTube.%20FYI%3A%20the%20full%20interview%20was%20released%20by%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20Neena%20Gupta's%20fearless%20attitude%2C%20a%20user%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20one%20of%20them%20who%20spits%20facts%20among%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20Courageous%20in%20a%20real%20sense....%C2%A0%20She%20honestly%20says%20what%20she%20feels%2Ffelt..She%20never%20hides%20it...never%20tries%20to%20sugarcoat%20it%20to%20project%20something%20much%20better....In%20short%20She%20doesn't%20fake...very%20genuine%20human%20.....%20It's%20all%20the%20bitter%20truth%20that%20everyone%20feels%20at%20certain%20point%20in%20their%20life....%26amp%3B%20she%20very%20accurately%20pinpoints%20these...%20that's%20why%20mostly%20people%20can%20relate%20to%20it...Lots%20of%20Lovvvvvvv%20to%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20a%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20few%20didn't%20agree%20with%20Neena%20Gupta's%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3Efaltu%3C%2Fi%3E%20feminism%E2%80%9D%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFeminism%20is%20not%20about%20men%20being%20pregnant%20or%20women%20bodybuilding!!%20But%20equal%20rights%20!!%20It's%20not%20faltu%20!!%20%26quot%3BFake%20Feminism%26quot%3B%20is%20faltu%20..%20but%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20Feminism%20is%20having%20equal%20rights%20and%20opportunities%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20a%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CFeminism%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20ideology.%20Like%20%26quot%3Bdemocracy%26quot%3B%20this%20too%20is%20misappropriated%20and%20misinterpreted%20by%20many%20including%20%26quot%3Bicon%26quot%3B%20Neena%20Gupta.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20a%20similar%20sentiment%2C%20this%20user%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20feminism%20talks%20of%20equality%20it%20does%20not%20claim%20biological%20identity.%20It%20claims%20cerebral%20opportunity%2C%20opportunity%20to%20have%20equal%20say%20in%20financial%20matters%20both%20in%20domestic%20and%20in%20private%2C%20equality%20to%20opportunities%20to%20positions%20like%20CEO%20etc.%20Please%20try%20to%20refrain%20from%20commenting%20on%20topics%20that%20you%20have%20skewed%20knowledge%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCalls%20feminism%20useless..then%20carries%20on%20to%20say%20that%20being%20a%20woman%20is%20the%20worst%20part%20of%20her%20life...I%20guess%20she%20never%20questioned%20why%20it's%20the%20worst.%20My%20god%2C%20the%20irony%20and%20hypocrisy.%20I%20give%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrust%20me%20feminism%20is%20a%20fake%20concept%20that%20fools%20many%20women.%20But%20a%20woman%20should%20believe%20in%20herself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC0HKERRikev%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC0HKERRikev%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC0HKERRikev%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%2