ed%22%3A1701062580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-uss-mason-vessel_6373832.jpg%3F20231127061504%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fus-warship-aids-israeli-linked-tanker-after-attack-in-gulf-of-aden-13017251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20ballistic%20missiles%20fired%20from%20Houthi-controlled%20Yemen%20came%20near%20a%20US%20warship%20after%20it%20aided%20an%20Israel-linked%20tanker%20that%20had%20been%20seized%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%2C%20the%20US%20military%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A104%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fus-warship-aids-israeli-linked-tanker-after-attack-in-gulf-of-aden-13017251%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fus-warship-aids-israeli-linked-tanker-after-attack-in-gulf-of-aden-13017251%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fus-warship-aids-israeli-linked-tanker-after-attack-in-gulf-of-aden-13017251%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%3A%20EC%20Withdraws%20Nod%20to%20BRS%20to%20Disburse%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20Scheme.%20What%20Does%20This%20Mean%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27104450%2FF_xPND0a4AA05Q0.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20withdrawn%20permission%20to%20the%20Telangana%20government%20to%20disburse%20Rs%207%2C350%20crore%20under%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20to%20nearly%2060%20lakh%20agricultural%20land-owning%20farmers%20after%20initially%20giving%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20shall%20be%20no%20disbursement%20under%20the%20Scheme%20till%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Telangana%20ceases%20to%20apply%20in%20all%20its%20forms%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20EC%20has%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20state%20will%20vote%20on%20November%2030%20and%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20panel%20noted%20that%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20finance%20minister%20who%20is%20also%20the%20BRS%20candidate%20for%20the%20Siddipet%20seat%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20not%20only%20violated%20the%20provisions%20of%20MCC%20contained%20in%20in%20Para%20VIl%20of%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20but%20also%20conditions%20laid%20down%20as%20above%20by%20publicising%20the%20release%20under%20the%20scheme%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20welfare%20distribution%20via%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer%20was%20thought%20as%20capable%20of%20significantly%20influencing%20the%20electoral%20outcome%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rastra%20Samithi%20(BRS).%20The%20authorisation%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20had%20raised%20questions%2C%20as%20its%20significance%20and%20the%20necessity%20for%20immediate%20implementation%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20possible%20delay%20by%20two%20weeks%2C%20had%20been%20initially%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20gave%20its%20nod%20to%20disburse%20the%20rabi%20instalment%20of%20Rythu%20Bandhu%2C%20an%20input%20subsidy%20scheme%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20was%20in%20force.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20was%20asked%20not%20to%20publicise%20the%20disbursement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Rao%20publicly%20announced%20the%20release%20of%20the%20rabi%20instalment%2C%20reportedly%20saying%20it%20would%20happen%20on%20Monday.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20before%20the%20farmers%20complete%20their%20breakfast%20and%20tea%2C%20the%20amount%20will%20be%20credited%20into%20their%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-orders-telangana-govt-to-stop-all-disbursements-under-rythu-bandhu-scheme-101701057664804.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2020%20flood%20relief%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%202020%20municipal%20elections%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20chief%20minister%20KCR%20announced%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20every%20household%20affected%20by%20urban%20floods%20caused%20by%20heavy%20rains%20during%20the%20election%20season.%20The%20decision%20to%20announce%20the%20flood%20relief%20through%20DBT%20was%20supposed%20to%20pacify%20voters%20with%20%E2%80%98an%20election%20gift%E2%80%99%20in%20view%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20BJP%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20politics%20over%20the%20announcement%20of%20DBT%20before%20elections%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fcities%2Fhyderabad%2Fstory%2Fpolitics-erupts-over-flood-relief-in-hyderabad-ahead-of-civic-body-elections-1736303-2020-10-29%5C%22%3Eopposed%20by%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20BJP.%20The%20Telangana%20State%20Election%20Commission%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FHyderabad%2Fec-slams-brakes-on-flood-relief-grant%2Farticle33127742.ece%5C%22%3Estopped%20this%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0mid-way%20with%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20exercise%20was%20stopped%2C%206.64%20lakh%20families%20received%20flood%20relief%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20664%20crore%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20Telangana%20State%20Election%20Commission%20asked%20the%20Government%20of%20Telangana%20to%20distribute%20the%20flood%20relief%20after%20the%20elections%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fin-other-news%2F081220%2Fghmc-officials-take-u-turn-on-rs-10000-flood-relief.html%5C%22%3Ewhich%20did%20not%20happen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20DBT%20announcement%20for%20flood%20relief%20was%20clearly%20made%20to%20ensure%20voters%20were%20not%20angry%20with%20BRS%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20vote%20against%20them%20in%20municipal%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Telangana%20State%20Election%20Commission%2C%20responsible%20for%20holding%20municipal%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20acted%20responsibly%20and%20delayed%20the%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20allow%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Assembly%20election%20cycle%20is%20clearly%20not%20rational.%20Anticipating%20such%20tactics%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-congress-demands-release-of-welfare-scheme-funds-before-nov-2-101698321542573.html%5C%22%3EIndian%20National%20Congress%20already%20demanded%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20ensure%20all%20welfare%20schemes%20linked%20to%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer%20programmes%20including%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20were%20completed%20by%20early%20November%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20relief%20for%20landless%20farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20likely%20to%20challenge%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20or%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20is%20unclear%20whether%20they%20would%20get%20the%20relief%20before%20the%20Government%20of%20Telangana%20transfers%20the%20money.%20BRS%20and%20Congress%20are%20likely%20going%20to%20accuse%20each%20other%20of%20opposing%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20welfare%20in%20itself%20is%20not%20wrong%20and%20the%20Congress%20too%20has%20promised%20a%20higher%20amount%20under%20Rythu%20Bandhu%2C%20including%20the%20relief%20for%20tenant%20farmers%2C%20who%20had%20been%20excluded%20under%20BRS%20government.%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20how%20it%20was%20being%20used%20to%20transfer%20money%20to%20large%20landowners%20while%20ignoring%20the%20landless%20farmers.%20This%20is%20a%20conscious%20decision%20under%20KCR%20to%20keep%20the%20landowning%20classes%20happy.%20It%20is%20also%20important%20to%20understand%20these%20decisions%20are%20backed%20by%20data%20that%20is%20not%20entirely%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20numbers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Ftelangana-samagraha-kumtumba-survey%5C%22%3EIntensive%20Household%20Survey%2F%20Samagraha%20Kutumba%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0data%2C%20In%20Telangana%2C%2068%25%20of%20households%20are%20landless%2C%20while%20the%20majority%20of%2032%25%20landowning%20classes%20only%20have%200-1%20acre%20of%20land.%20The%20land%20ownership-based%20welfare%20programme%20has%20been%20only%20helping%20the%20rich%20landowner%2C%20who%20receive%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20acre.%20Most%20of%20the%2068%25%20landless%20households%20are%20from%20Backward%20Classes%20with%2033%2C36%2C524%20households%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20own%20land%2C%2011%2C99%2C015%20households%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%2011%2C63%2C250%20households%20belonging%20to%20minorities%2C%20and%204%2C62%2C829%20households%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-us.googleusercontent.com%2F0ssk7OtAXWhMazIk4m0sEJQEA_WG0Z_n1iN-6n6cglg3Gt96cwXBIRkGqobWZUyqPV7rMH2nmaTz8sHR11RU-BytoEwBNTKIhmwoUfTMSymN1aJjNveGo4At5X0IDSLJIvCsOvWTjaBCLe0FC-CgEj0%5C%22%20data-ll-status%3D%5C%22loaded%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20data-lazy-src%3D%5C%22%2F%2Flh7-us.googleusercontent.com%2F0ssk7OtAXWhMazIk4m0sEJQEA_WG0Z_n1iN-6n6cglg3Gt96cwXBIRkGqobWZUyqPV7rMH2nmaTz8sHR11RU-BytoEwBNTKIhmwoUfTMSymN1aJjNveGo4At5X0IDSLJIvCsOvWTjaBCLe0FC-CgEj0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELand%20Ownership%20in%20Telangana%20Source%3A%20Intensive%20Household%20Survey%20%2F%20Samagraha%20Kutumba%20Survey%202014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-us.googleusercontent.com%2FLlafvJ_46GTRDmxJbLJHSbU-NO8k9d-Yo2q6tfX-SYIT5xVHfGUsGjx6gG5afafK9p0IOoyVzPmooN3gAwrSqsxb8l5kQ21mlcOAsypU_tnMBj8TRhALl2R4uKAZEXEnrAzsve4_HKYUOA9_OcF4MDQ%5C%22%20data-ll-status%3D%5C%22loaded%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20data-lazy-src%3D%5C%22%2F%2Flh7-us.googleusercontent.com%2FLlafvJ_46GTRDmxJbLJHSbU-NO8k9d-Yo2q6tfX-SYIT5xVHfGUsGjx6gG5afafK9p0IOoyVzPmooN3gAwrSqsxb8l5kQ21mlcOAsypU_tnMBj8TRhALl2R4uKAZEXEnrAzsve4_HKYUOA9_OcF4MDQ%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELandless%20Household%20in%20Telangana%20Source%3A%20Intensive%20Household%20Survey%2FSamagraha%20Kutumba%20Survey%202014%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDirect%20Benefit%20Transfer%20helps%20political%20parties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20utilisation%20of%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer%20(DBT)%20facilitated%20by%20Aadhaar%20appears%20to%20advantage%20incumbent%20political%20parties%20by%20swiftly%20disbursing%20financial%20benefits%20to%20the%20populace%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20DBT%2C%20a%20system%20powered%20through%20the%20Aadhaar%20payment%20bridge%2C%20operates%20as%20both%20a%20monetary%20mechanism%20and%20a%20micro-targeting%20system%2C%20although%20the%20specifics%20of%20group%20targeting%20remain%20opaque.%20During%20the%202019%20General%20Elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20mirrored%20this%20strategy%20by%20launching%20PM-KISAN%2C%20inspired%20by%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20opposition%20struggles%20with%20organising%20its%20political%20stance%2C%20DBT%20enables%20ruling%20parties%20to%20leverage%20governmental%20machinery%20for%20electoral%20gains.%20When%20combined%20with%20Aadhaar%2C%20DBT%20allows%20the%20government%20to%20identify%20beneficiaries%20and%20empowers%20political%20parties%20to%20canvass%20votes%20from%20these%20specific%20recipients.%20The%20BRS%20workers%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20can%20approach%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20beneficiaries%2C%20seeking%20their%20support%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20the%20opposition%20largely%20lacks%20access%20to%20beneficiary%20information%20and%20the%20outcomes%20of%20the%20Samagraha%20Kutumba%20Survey%2FIntensive%20Household%20Survey%20conducted%20in%202014.%20Conversely%2C%20as%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20KCR%20and%20the%20BRS%20have%20access%20to%20non-public%20information%20sources%2C%20providing%20them%20an%20edge%20in%20understanding%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20population%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapitalising%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20revelations%20from%20the%20Cambridge%20Analytica%20whistleblower%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20exposing%20the%20manipulation%20of%20data%20for%20electoral%20purposes%20worldwide%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20this%20matter%20continues%20to%20impact%20Indian%20elections%20without%20any%20evident%20plan%20to%20counter%20algorithmic%20manipulation%20and%20targeting%20during%20elections.%20The%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20decision%20to%20allow%20DBT%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20an%20election%20cycle%20could%20have%20been%20poised%20to%20disproportionately%20favour%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20Aadhaar%20in%20constructing%20comprehensive%20Big%20Data%20repositories%20for%20micro-targeting%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20DBT%20for%20financial%20welfare%20programme%20is%20significantly%20undervalued.%20Big%20Data%20and%20substantial%20financial%20resources%20are%20employed%20to%20influence%20the%20population%20beyond%20electoral%20cycles%2C%20posing%20concerns%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20safeguards%20and%20discussions%20addressing%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20methods%20observed%20in%20the%20Telangana%20assembly%20elections%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20replicated%20and%20expanded%20upon%20in%20national%20elections.%C2%A0%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20pressing%20need%20to%20hold%20the%20Election%20Commission%20accountable%20for%20its%20practices%20and%20clarify%20the%20rationale%20behind%20permitting%20substantial%20monetary%20transfers%20during%20electoral%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20article%20was%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siasat.com%2Frythu-bandhu-how-dbt-sways-elections-in-favour-of-incumbents-2919986%2F%5C%22%3ESiasat%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20was%20updated%20and%20republished%20under%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby-nd%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ECreative%20Commons%20licence.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701062211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27104450%2FF_xPND0a4AA05Q0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frythu-bandhu-scheme-election-commission-brs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20welfare%20distribution%20via%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer%20was%20thought%20as%20capable%20of%20significantly%20influencing%20the%20electoral%20outcome%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rastra%20Samithi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frythu-bandhu-scheme-election-commission-brs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zhongzhi%20Enterprise%20Group%3A%20China%20investigates%20major%20shadow%20bank%20for%20'crimes'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701061284000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5DFE%2Fproduction%2F_131826042_gettyimages-1241969189.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw