g%20interest%20rates%20often%20higher%20than%201%2C000%25%20yearly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2022-02-10%2Ftrump-freed-jon-braun-from-prison-now-loan-shark-is-back-in-business%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20telephone%20interview%20with%20the%20Times%2C%20Braun%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%20as%20a%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20after%20his%202011%20drug%20smuggling%20conviction%2C%20Braun%20was%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20in%20a%20New%20York%20prison%20despite%20cooperating%20with%20investigators.%20He%20began%20his%20sentence%20in%202020%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fag.ny.gov%2Fpress-release%2F2020%2Fattorney-general-james-sues-predatory-lender-threatened-violence-and-kidnapping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENY%20State%20AG%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Braun's%20hand%20in%20the%20lending%20industry%20made%20him%20a%20valuable%20asset%20to%20the%20Justice%20Department%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Times%2C%20since%20the%20US%20attorney's%20office%20in%20Manhattan%20was%20investigating%20the%20wider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhow-one-ex-predatory-lender-has-turned-his-life-around-to-help-businesses-find-relief-from-merchant-cash-debt-and-avoid-bankruptcy-1029917616%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredatory%20lending%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Braun's%20experience%2C%20the%20DOJ%20hoped%20to%20cut%20out%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20convicted%20smuggler%20by%20commuting%20his%20sentence%20in%20exchange%20for%20providing%20information%20on%20other%20predatory%20lenders%20and%20possibly%20wearing%20a%20wire%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20deal%20would%20fall%20apart%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-calls-for-death-penalty-drug-dealers-despite-pardoning-some-2022-9%5C%22%20ta