0job%20is%20to%20fix%20the%20economy.%20We%20have%20to%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20get%20inflation%20under%20control%20so%20we%20can%20lower%20interest%20rates%20and%20make%20food%20more%20affordable%2C%26quot%3B%20Luxon%20said.%20The%20newly%20formed%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20revoke%20its%20groundbreaking%20anti-smoking%20law%2C%20which%20was%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20future%20generations%20from%20smoking%2C%20in%20order%20to%20finance%20tax%20reductions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnew-zealands-new-government-sworn-in-scraps-world-first-smoking-generation-ban%2Farticleshow%2F105524477.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnew-zealands-new-government-sworn-in-scraps-world-first-smoking-generation-ban%2Famp_articleshow%2F105524477.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnew-zealands-new-government-sworn-in-scraps-world-first-smoking-generation-ban%2Famp_articleshow%2F105524477.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20the%20List%20of%20Palestinians%20Released%20in%20the%20Exchange%20Says%20About%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27093258%2FF_uue79W8AAJQNu.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Hamas%20are%20acting%20on%20an%20agreement%20to%20pause%20hostilities%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20nearly%20seven%20weeks%20into%20the%20war.%20The%20deal%20included%20a%20four-day%20ceasefire%20and%20an%20exchange%20of%2050%20Israeli%20hostages%20for%20150%20Palestinian%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20prisoners%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20further%20exchanges%20thereafter.%20These%20are%20terms%20that%20Hamas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fnov%2F09%2Fnetanyahu-rejected-ceasefire-for-hostages-deal-in-gaza-sources-say%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20offered%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Israel%20weeks%20ago%20in%20the%20early%20phases%20of%20the%20war%2C%20but%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20preferred%20to%20wage%20an%20all-out%20assault%20on%20the%20besieged%20Strip%2C%20killing%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20before%20considering%20a%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20even%20at%20the%20detriment%20of%20the%20safety%20and%20wellbeing%20of%20the%20Israeli%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.il%2Fhe%2FDepartments%2FDynamicCollectors%2Fis-db%3Fskip%3D0%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20names%20of%20300%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20that%20it%20is%20considering%20releasing%20as%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20or%20upon%20the%20freeing%20of%20more%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20in%20order%20to%20allow%20for%20legal%20appeals%20in%20Israeli%20courts%20against%20the%20release%20of%20specific%20individuals.%20All%20of%20the%20hostages%20and%20prisoners%20to%20be%20exchanged%20at%20this%20stage%20are%20women%20and%20minors.%20Still%2C%20many%20among%20the%20Israeli%20right%2C%20and%20perhaps%20the%20wider%20public%2C%20believe%20that%20the%20government%20is%20making%20a%20significant%20concession%20by%20releasing%20dangerous%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20few%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20through%20the%20list%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20slated%20for%20release%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20strikes%20you%20is%20their%20ages.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fisrael-publishes-details-of-palestinian-prisoners-to-be-released-as-part-of-hostage-deal%2F%5C%22%3E287%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20aged%2018%20or%20under%2C%20including%20five%20as%20young%20as%2014%2C%20which%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20how%20does%20a%2014-year-old%20boy%20become%20a%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20prisoner%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20on%20the%20list%20include%20alleged%20members%20of%20Palestinian%20political%20factions%20like%20Hamas%2C%20Fatah%2C%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20and%20the%20Popular%20Front%20for%20the%20Liberation%20of%20Palestine%20(PFLP)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20many%20who%20are%20not%20affiliated%20with%20any%20group.%20None%20were%20convicted%20of%20murder.%20Some%20were%20convicted%20of%20attempted%20murder%2C%20while%20the%20majority%20were%20charged%20with%20less%20significant%20offences%2C%20including%20a%20large%20number%20who%20were%20arrested%20for%20throwing%20stones.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20a%2017-year-old%2C%20has%20been%20behind%20bars%20for%20two%20years%20for%20throwing%20stones%20at%20an%20Israeli%20police%20vehicle%20in%20Jerusalem%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20city%20where%20Jewish%20settlers%20can%20carry%20out%20riots%20against%20Palestinians%20that%20rarely%20end%20in%20investigations%2C%20let%20alone%20arrests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20all%2C%20the%20list%20is%20a%20dizzying%20testament%20to%20just%20how%20central%20detention%20and%20imprisonment%20are%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20and%20control%20over%20Palestinians.%20According%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhamoked.org.il%2Fprisoners-charts.php%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20group%20HaMoked%2C%20as%20of%20November%202023%2C%20Israel%20holds%206%2C809%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20prisoners.%E2%80%9D%20Of%20these%2C%202%2C313%20are%20serving%20a%20prison%20sentence%3B%202%2C321%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20convicted%20in%20court%3B%202%2C070%20are%20being%20held%20under%20administrative%20detention%20(indefinitely%20imprisoned%20without%20trial%20or%20due%20process)%3B%20and%20105%20are%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20combatants%E2%80%9D%20who%20were%20arrested%20during%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20October%207%20attacks%20in%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20of%20the%20300%20Palestinians%20considered%20for%20release%20are%20relatively%20new%20prisoners%2C%20arrested%20in%20the%20last%20year%20or%20two.%20The%20exceptions%20are%2010%20women%20from%20Jerusalem%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20who%20have%20been%20imprisoned%20since%202015-17%2C%20most%20of%20them%20on%20charges%20of%20attempting%20or%20committing%20stabbing%20attacks%20against%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20ended%20without%20any%20harm%2C%20while%20others%20caused%20minor%20to%20moderate%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%2C%20it%20should%20be%20recalled%2C%20is%20overseen%20by%20the%20same%20judicial%20system%20that%2C%20among%20countless%20other%20examples%2C%20decided%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fsettler-stabbed-killed-ali-harb%2F%5C%22%3Eclose%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0against%20an%20Israeli%20settler%20who%20stabbed%20a%20young%20Palestinian%20to%20death%20in%20May%202022%20because%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20rule%20out%20%5Bthe%20suspect%E2%80%99s%5D%20version%20that%20he%20acted%20in%20self-defense.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20the%20same%20system%20that%2C%20in%20July%20of%20this%20year%2C%20acquitted%20an%20Israeli%20police%20officer%20who%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fiyad-al-hallaq-police-court-acquittal%2F%5C%22%3Eshot%20dead%20Iyad%20al-Hallaq%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20autistic%20Palestinian%20man%2C%20despite%20clear%20testimonies%20and%20video%20evidence%20proving%20he%20was%20unarmed%20and%20made%20no%20threat%20of%20any%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Palestinian%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20prisoners%E2%80%9D%20are%20judged%20in%20a%20separate%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Ftopic%2Fmilitary-courts%2F%5C%22%3Emilitary%20court%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20boasts%20a%20conviction%20rate%20of%20between%2095%20to%2099%20percent.%C2%A0Lenience%2C%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20Israeli%20apartheid%20regime%2C%20is%20a%20right%20reserved%20for%20Jews%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jews%20who%20riot%2C%20attack%2C%20and%20even%20kill%20Palestinians%20are%20immune%20from%20prosecution%2C%20the%20prisoners%20list%20reminds%20us%20that%20Palestinians%20can%20be%20arrested%20wholesale%20based%20solely%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintention%E2%80%9D%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20violent%20act.%20One%20of%20those%20on%20the%20list%2C%20a%2045-year-old%20woman%20from%20Jerusalem%2C%20has%20been%20in%20prison%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%20because%20%E2%80%9Cshe%20was%20caught%20in%20the%20Old%20City%20with%20a%20knife%20in%20her%20hand%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csaid%20that%20she%20intended%20to%20carry%20out%20an%20attack.%E2%80%9D%20Meanwhile%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Kahanist%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fben-gvir-ministry-kahane%2F%5C%22%3Enational%20security%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20urging%20Jews%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fguns-israel-america-supremacy%2F%5C%22%3Earm%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0while%20handing%20out%20weapons%20like%20candy%2C%20and%20many%20right-wing%20Israelis%20are%20writing%20countless%20messages%2C%20in%20public%20and%20private%2C%20gleefully%20announcing%20their%20intention%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmurder%20as%20many%20Arabs%20as%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometimes%20%E2%80%9Cintent%E2%80%9D%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20appear%20on%20the%20list%20of%20charges.%20An%2018-year-old%20from%20Jerusalem%20was%20%E2%80%9Carrested%20along%20with%20others%20because%20he%20cried%20out%20%E2%80%98Allahu%20Akbar.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20An%2018-year-old%20woman%20from%20the%20West%20Bank%20has%20been%20imprisoned%20for%20months%20for%20%E2%80%9Cincitement%20on%20Instagram.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20Israeli%20public%20in%20contrast%2C%20explicit%20calls%20for%20genocide%20are%20considered%20a%20legitimate%20way%20to%20raise%20the%20national%20morale%2C%20while%20Palestinians%20with%20Israeli%20citizenship%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.co.il%2Fnews%2Flaw%2F2023-10-30%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2F0000018b-7c89-d4a8-a3cf-fca967310000%5C%22%3Emay%20be%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20posting%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20a%20photo%20of%20shakshuka%20next%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20indictments%20listed%2C%20only%20a%20few%20are%20related%20to%20the%20use%20of%20weapons%20and%20opening%20fire%20on%20Israeli%20forces%20(and%20even%20in%20these%20cases%2C%20there%20were%20no%20fatalities).%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20incidents%20involve%20throwing%20stones%20or%20Molotov%20cocktails%2C%20shooting%20fireworks%2C%20and%20causing%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20disorder.%E2%80%9D%20Was%20it%20worth%20letting%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%2C%20languish%20in%20Gaza%20for%20a%20few%20more%20weeks%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20continuing%20to%20imprison%20a%20young%20man%20who%20dared%20to%20cry%20%E2%80%9CGod%20is%20great%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20this%20list%20is%20composed%20of%20%E2%80%9Csoft%E2%80%9D%20prisoners%2C%20who%20won%E2%80%99t%20arouse%20as%20much%20public%20opposition%2C%20while%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20who%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20far%20more%20severe%20and%20deadly%20crimes%20remain%20in%20Israeli%20jails.%20But%20the%20300%20names%20that%20Israel%20was%20able%20to%20put%20together%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20young%2C%20arrested%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20and%20doing%20time%20for%20some%20form%20of%20popular%20resistance%20%E2%80%94%20should%20lead%20to%20some%20reflection%20among%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20after%20all%2C%20a%20clear%20connection%20between%20the%20heavy-handed%20suppression%20of%20any%20expression%20of%20Palestinian%20opposition%2C%20and%20the%20strengthening%20of%20armed%20groups%20that%20see%20violence%20as%20the%20only%20way%20to%20seriously%20challenge%20their%20occupiers.%20But%20this%20would%20require%20the%20Israeli%20public%20to%20finally%20grasp%20the%20basic%20fact%20that%20as%20long%20as%20oppression%20continues%2C%20resistance%20will%20inevitably%20continue%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%2B972.%20Read%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fpalestinian-prisoners-israeli-hostages-exchange%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20version%20of%20this%20article%20first%20appeared%20in%20Hebrew%20on%20%3C%2Fi%3ELocal%20Call%3Ci%3E.%20Read%20it%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mekomit.co.il%2F%25d7%2590%25d7%2599%25d7%259a-%25d7%2599%25d7%259c%25d7%2593-%25d7%2591%25d7%259f-14-%25d7%2594%25d7%2595%25d7%25a4%25d7%259a-%25d7%259c%25d7%2590%25d7%25a1%25d7%2599%25d7%25a8-%25d7%2591%25d7%2599%25d7%2598%25d7%2597%25d7%2595%25d7%25a0%25d7%2599-%25d7%2591%25d7%25a7%25d7%259c%25d7%2595%25d7%25aa-%25d7%25a8%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Ehere%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20has%20been%20edited%20slightly%20for%20tense.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOrly%20Noy%20is%20an%20editor%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3ELocal%20Call%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20political%20activist%2C%20and%20a%20translator%20of%20Farsi%20poetry%20and%20prose.%20She%20is%20the%20chair%20of%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%E2%80%99s%20executive%20board%20and%20an%20activist%20with%20the%20Balad%20political%20party.%20Her%20writing%20deals%20with%20the%20lines%20that%20intersect%20and%20define%20her%20identity%20as%20Mizrahi%2C%20a%20female%20leftist%2C%20a%20woman%2C%20a%20temporary%20migrant%20living%20inside%20a%20perpetual%20immigrant%2C%20and%20the%20constant%20dialogue%20between%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C