d%20Israelis%20trusting%20the%20security%20establishment%20to%20lead%20the%20war%20effort%2C%20but%20not%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20failure%20of%20Oct.%207%20is%20his%20legacy.%20Whatever%20success%20Israel%20will%20have%20in%20the%20aftermath%20will%20not%20be%20ascribed%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetanyahu%20Vows%20To%20Control%20Security%20In%20Gaza%20Indefinitely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20has%20vowed%20to%20control%20security%20in%20Gaza%20indefinitely%2C%20adding%20uncertainty%20to%20the%20fate%20of%20an%20enclave%20where%20for%20seven%20weeks%20Israel%20was%20on%20the%20attack%20before%20forging%20a%20temporary%20truce%20with%20Hamas%20and%20the%20freeing%20of%20hostages%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Palestinian%20detainees%20from%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2014%2C800%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20war%2C%20Gaza%20health%20authorities%20say%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20longest-serving%20prime%20minister%2C%20Netanyahu%20has%20survived%20many%20a%20political%20crisis%2C%20staged%20several%20comebacks%2C%20and%20need%20not%20face%20another%20election%20for%20three%20years%20if%20his%20coalition%20remains%20in%20tact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20him%20very%20well%20and%20he%20concentrates%20on%20what%20he%20is%20doing%2C%20he%20is%20really%20a%20very%20hard-working%20person%20and%20now%20he%20is%20running%20a%20war%20and%20he%20is%20holding%2C%20like%20a%20juggler%2C%20half-a-dozen%20balls%20in%20the%20air%20-%20and%20to%20keep%20them%20only%20in%20the%20air%20he%20must%20concentrate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abraham%20Diskin%2C%20professor%20emeritus%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Jerusalem's%20Hebrew%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20go%20out%20and%20face%20people%20who%20shout%20at%20you%20and%20really%20hate%20you%2C%20there%20is%20no%20benefit%20of%20doing%20that%2C%20so%20he%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Diskin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGantz%20In%20Cabinet%20Offers%20Netanyahu%20Stability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlim%2C%20tall%20and%20blue-eyed%20with%20an%20easy%20way%20about%20him%2C%20Gantz%2C%2064%2C%20joined%20an%20Israeli%20war%20cabinet%20that%20Netanyahu%20formed%20days%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20to%20unite%20the%20country%20behind%20a%20campaign%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20retrieve%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20nearly%2040%20years%20in%20the%20military%2C%20the%20centrist%20Gantz%20offers%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20rightist%20Likud%20party%20a%20more%20stable%20government%20that%20reduces%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20far-right%20and%20religious%20coalition%20partners%20on%20the%20fringes%20of%20Israeli%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnited%20in%20war%20perhaps%2C%20they%20are%20at%20odds%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20Netanyahu%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20of%20Likud%20have%20together%20held%20press%20conferences.%20A%20photo%20of%20one%20such%20event%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20captured%20Netanyahu%20alone%2C%20and%20Gallant%20and%20Gantz%20standing%20together%20off%20to%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Nov.%2016%20opinion%20poll%20found%20the%20Netanyahu-led%20coalition%20that%20won%2064%20seats%20in%20a%20November%202022%20election%20would%20garner%2045%20in%20the%20120-member%20Knesset%20today%20compared%20with%2070%20seats%20of%20parties%20led%20by%20Gantz's%20National%20Unity%20Party%2C%20enough%20to%20assume%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20for%20Israel's%20Channel%2012%20took%20place%20a%20week%20before%20Qatar%20announced%20the%20hostage%20deal%20and%20was%20conducted%20among%20502%20respondents%20by%20pollster%20Mano%20Geva%20and%20the%20company%20Midgam%20and%20had%20a%20margin%20of%20error%20of%204.4%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGantz%20has%20little%20of%20Netany