Gulf%20of%20Aden.%20US%20Navy%20pursued%20toward%20Yemen.%20Warning%20shots%20fired.%20Gunmen%20now%20being%20interrogated.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jennifer%20Griffin%20(%40JenGriffinFNC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJenGriffinFNC%2Fstatus%2F1728918334044024929%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Griffin%2C%20the%20official%20also%20stated%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-building-warships-to-counter-north-korean-missile-threat-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapanese%20destroyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20the%20US%20Navy%20while%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-navy-six-highly-capable-vessels-middle-east-military-expert-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20Navy%20warships%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20vicinity%20did%20not%20render%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gunmen%20exited%20the%20vehicle%20and%20were%20sailing%20back%20to%20Yemen%20shores%20when%20US%20Navy%20personnel%20made%20the%20arrest%2C%20Griffin%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20and%20coalition%20forces%20responded%20to%20a%20distress%20call%20from%20the%20M%2FV%20Central%20Park.%20The%20crew%20of%20the%20M%2FV%20Central%20Park%20is%20currently%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20US%20defense%20official%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20did%20not%20address%20questions%20regarding%20the%20details%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20including%20whether%205%20armed%20gunmen%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%20and%20if%20Chinese%20Navy%20ships%20were%20near%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZodiac%20Maritime%20has%20been%20targeted%20previously%20amid%20a%20wider%20yearslong%20shadow%20war%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel.%20In%202021%2C%20a%20drone%20attack%20assessed%20by%20the%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20nations%20to%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20Iran%20killed%20two%20crew%20members%20aboard%20Zodiac's%20oil%20tanker%20Mercer%20Street%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Oman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20military's%20United%20Kingdom%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%2C%20which%20provides%20warnings%20to%20sailors%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20had%20earlier%20warned%20sailors%20that%20%26quot%3Btwo%20black-and-white%20craft%20carrying%20eight%20persons%20in%20military-style%20clothing%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20area.%20It%20issued%20another%20warning%2C%20saying%20that%20radio%20traffic%20suggested%20a%20possible%20attack%20had%20occurred%20before%20acknowledging%20the%20seizure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UKMTO%20put%20the%20ship's%20location%20over%2060%20kilometers%20(35%20miles)%20south%20of%20Yemen's%20coast%2C%20some%2080%20kilometers%20(50%20miles)%20east%20of%20Djibouti%2C%20and%20about%20110%20kilometers%20(70%20miles)%20northeast%20of%20Somalia%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%2C%20a%20key%20shipping%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Park%20seizure%20comes%20after%20a%20container%20ship%2C%20CMA%20CGM%20Symi%2C%20owned%20by%20another%20Israeli%20billionaire%2C%20came%20under%20attack%20Friday%20by%20a%20suspected%20Iranian%20drone%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20Iran%20has%20not%20acknowledged%20carrying%20out%20the%20attack%2C%20nor%20did%20it%20respond%20to%20questions%20from%20the%20AP%20about%20that%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Symi%20and%20the%20Central%20Park%20had%20been%20behaving%20as%20if%20they%20faced%20a%20threat%20in%20recent%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ships%20had%20switched%20off%20their%20Automatic%20Identification%20System%20trackers%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20MarineTraffic.com%20analyzed%20by%20the%20AP.%20Ships%20are%20supposed%20to%20keep%20their%20AIS%20active%20for%20safety%20reasons%2C%20but%20crews%20will%20turn%20them%20off%20if%20they%20appear%20to%20be%20targeted.%20In%20Central%20Park's%20case%2C%20the%20vessel%20had%20last%20transmitted%20four%20days%20a