%20that%20he%20was%20being%20implicated%20in%20the%20case%2C%20per%20the%20PTI%20report.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20central%20investigating%20agency%20forced%20him%20to%20sign%20a%20statement%20in%20English%2C%20a%20language%20he%20does%20not%20understand%2C%20Das%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Shoaib%20Alvi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20Das%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20visited%20Dubai%20twice%20in%20October%20this%20year%20after%20being%20called%20there%20by%20Shubham%20Soni%2C%20a%20childhood%20friend%2C%20to%20talk%20about%20some%20investments%20in%20a%20construction%20business.%20The%20trips%20were%20arranged%20by%20Soni%2C%20he%20said.%20Soni%2C%20per%20the%20ED%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDas%20has%20also%20claimed%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20on%20the%20day%20of%20his%20arrest%2C%20and%20after%20his%20arrival%20in%20Raipur%20airport%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20car%20parked%20in%20the%20airport%E2%80%99s%20parking%20lot%20and%20check%20into%20a%20hotel%20on%20VIP%20road%20in%20the%20city.%20Later%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20park%20on%20the%20road%20where%20a%20person%20put%20bags%20of%20cash%20in%20the%20car%20and%20left%3B%20Das%20was%20told%20via%20a%20phone%20call%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20hotel%20room.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20was%20when%20the%20ED%20officials%20came%20to%20his%20room%20and%20took%20him%20with%20them%2C%20Das%20claimed.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20later%20realised%20that%20he%20was%20being%20implicated%20and%20denied%20ever%20having%20supplied%20money%20or%20any%20other%20assistance%20to%20politicians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDas%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20admit%20the%20letter%20as%20part%20of%20the%20case%20record%2C%20PTI%20quoted%20Alvi%20as%20saying.%20The%20Raipur%20special%20court%20has%20extended%20Das%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20custody%20for%20an%20additional%20week%2C%20per%20the%20PTI%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConnections%20with%20CM%20Baghel%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-app-courier-who-named-bhupesh-baghel-backtracks-says-was-framed-4604561%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Das%20%E2%80%93%20with%20over%20Rs.%205%20crore%20in%20cash%20%E2%80%93%20on%20November%203%2C%20four%20days%20before%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20elections%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case.%20It%20claimed%20that%20forensic%20analysis%20and%20a%20statement%20by%20Das%20%E2%80%93%20on%20his%20own%20admission%20%E2%80%93%20had%20led%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstartling%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20promoters%20had%20paid%20Rs.%20508%20crore%20to%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%20On%20November%205%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20banned%2022%20softwares%20and%20websites%2C%20including%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app.%20Baghel%20had%20questioned%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctiming%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20being%20raked%20up%20to%20tarnish%20his%20image%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20had%20claimed%20that%20Das%20was%20allegedly%20sent%20by%20the%20app%20promoters%20from%20the%20UAE%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%2C%20to%20deliver%20large%20amount%20of%20cash%20for%20electioneering%20expenses%20of%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20Party%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CAsim%20Das%20has%20admitted%20that%20the%20seized%20funds%20were%20arranged%20by%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20promoters%20to%20be%20delivered%20to%20one%20politician%20%E2%80%98Baghel%E2%80%99%20for%20upcoming%20election%20expenses%20in%20state%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20had%20alleged%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20per%20a%20PTI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C