22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fai-firm-braiin-holdings-forays-into-india-plans-to-invest-100-million-123112600640_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20RSS-BJP%20Economic%20Development%20Model%3A%20Support%20the%20Upper%20Castes%20and%20Ignore%20Bahujans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F28164328%2FKokan-Farmer-Sindhudurg-Goa-Nature-Green-2795521.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20I%20wrote%20a%20piece%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhi-is-reshaping-congress-welfare-agenda-i-call-it-the-shudra-development-model%2F1845140%2F%5C%22%3Etitled%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%98Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20Reshaping%20Congress%20Welfare%20Agenda%3A%20I%20Call%20it%20the%20Shudra%20Development%20Model%E2%80%99%2C%20there%20has%20been%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20curiosity%20about%20what%20the%20Shudra%20Development%20Model%20(SDM)%2C%20Brahmin-Bania%20Development%20Model%20(BBDM)%20are.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%20there%20are%20broadly%20three%20development%20models%20that%20Indian%20economists%2C%20whether%20educated%20in%20India%20or%20abroad%2C%20talk%20and%20write%20about%3A%201.%20The%20liberal%20development%20model%3B%202.%20the%20neo-liberal%20development%20model%3B%20and%203.%20the%20socialist%20development%20model.%20The%20pro-Congress%20economists%2C%20till%20the%20globalisation%20and%20liberalisation%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20were%20bracketed%20as%20liberal%20economists%20and%20the%20pro-RSS%2FBJP%20economists%20were%20among%20the%20neo-liberals.%20Left-oriented%20economists%20were%20seen%20as%20backers%20of%20socialist%20development.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20hardly%20any%20indigenous%20economic%20model%20that%20was%20developed%20in%20the%20post-colonial%20economic%20discourse%20of%20India.%20The%20only%20concept%20that%20I%20know%20of%20is%20that%20the%20Indian%20economists%20used%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Fthe-history-behind-hindu-rate-of-growth-in-charts-11678370005198.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520term%2520%25E2%2580%259CHindu%2520rate%2520of%2Cwhen%2520it%2520averaged%2520around%25204%2525.%5C%22%3EHindu%20Rate%20of%20Growth%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99.%20This%20was%20used%20in%20the%20sense%20of%20a%20slow%20growth%20rate%20without%20any%20rational%20explanation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20an%20economist%20does%20not%20deal%20with%20the%20role%20of%20caste%20in%20determining%20the%20financial%20allocations%20from%20the%20state%20budget%20with%20a%20caste%20benefit%20perspective%2C%20they%2C%20whatever%20their%20own%20caste%20location%2C%20will%20do%20a%20caste-blind%20economic%20analysis%20and%20that%20would%20help%20the%20Dwija%20economy.%20The%20Dwija%20methods%20of%20garnering%20state%20money%20without%20being%20involved%20in%20any%20productive%20work%20is%20part%20of%20their%20caste%20ideology%20and%20varna%20dharma%20heritage.%20The%20spiritual%20system%20of%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20meant%20to%20keep%20the%20Dwijas%20well-fed%20and%20starve%20the%20food%20producers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20varna%20dharma%20state%20allocation%20of%20finances%20goes%20against%20the%20entire%20agrarian%20and%20artisanal%20economy%2C%20which%20I%20call%20the%20Shudra%20economy.%20The%20Shudra%20economy%20is%20structurally%20opposite%20to%20the%20Dwija%20economy.%20The%20Shudra%20economy%20mainly%20survives%20on%20agrarian%20and%20artisanal%20production%2C%20not%20on%20profit.%20Investing%20in%20labour%20on%20the%20land%20and%20producing%20food%20and%20other%20commodities%20is%20central%20to%20the%20Shudra%20ideology.%20The%20money%20for%20the%20state%20budget%20mostly%20comes%20from%20their%20activities.%20If%20it%20is%20not%20reinvested%20in%20those%20fields%20of%20production%2C%20the%20economy%20would%20get%20depressed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20Shudra%20forces%20become%20industrialists%2C%20their%20relationship%20to%20the%20agrarian%20economy%20would%20be%20sympathetic%20and%20interactive%20with%20labour%20and%20land.%20The%20Dwija%20industrialist%20consciousness%20is%20anti-Shudra%20and%20anti-agrarian.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Dwija%20economy%20survived%20and%20prospered%20only%20by%20looting%20the%20Shudra%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20economic%20resources%20for%20millennia%2C%20both%20through%20market%20and%20state%20apparatus.%20The%20development%20of%20Indian%20industry%20on%20a%20massive%20scale%20when%20the%20RSS-BJP%20came%20to%20power%20is%20more%20because%20the%20Government%20in%20Delhi%20is%20pushing%20the%20contract%20economy%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20Dwija%20industrialists%20by%20starving%20the%20agrarian%20sector%2C%20as%20it%20is%20mainly%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Shudra%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities.%20So%20far%2C%20no%20economic%20model%20has%20analysed%20and%20understood%20this%20systemic%20bias%20in%20the%20allocation%20of%20budget%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20RSS-BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20with%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESab%20Ka%20Sath%20and%20Sab%20Ka%20Vikas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20did%20the%20national%20state%20budget%20economy%20get%20spent%20in%20real%20terms%3F%20Whom%20did%20it%20develop%3F%20In%20caste-class%20terms%2C%20the%20agrarian%20and%20artisanal%20Shudra%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20masses%20hardly%20got%20any%20visible%20%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(development)%20with%20the%20resources%20allocated%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20Most%20of%20the%20central%20budget%20was%20spent%20on%20infrastructure%20like%20highways%2C%20big%20airports%2C%20Vande%20Bharat%2C%20etc.%20The%20RSS-BJP%20government%20is%20also%20spending%20money%20on%20building%20stadiums%20for%20global%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrivatisation%20of%20most%20government%20industrial%20units%20at%20cheaper%20rates%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20to%20Bania-Brahmin%20industrialists%20%E2%80%93%20has%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20reducing%20the%20reserved%20jobs%20for%20Dalit%2C%20Adivasi%20and%20OBC%20communities.%20The%20salaried%20incomes%20of%20persons%20from%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20communities%20employed%20in%20these%20sectors%20are%20also%20a%20source%20of%20investment%20in%20the%20rural%20agrarian%20and%20artisanal%20communities.%20By%20cutting%20down%20such%20reserved%20jobs%20the%20BJP-RSS%20Union%20government%20is%20directly%20helping%20the%20Brahmin-Bania%20rich%20and%20providing%20more%20jobs%20to%20youth%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Dwija%20families%20and%20educated%20in%20private%20sector%20schools%20and%20colleges%20in%20English%20medium.%20The%20RSS%2FBJP%20is%20opposing%20English%20medium%20in%20government%20sector%20education%2C%20where%20the%20children%20of%20agrarian%20and%20artisanal%20masses%20study.%20India%20is%20not%20going%20through%20a%20national%20economic%20depression%20but%20is%20going%20through%20a%20caste%20economic%20depression.%20This%20depression%20does%20not%20bother%20anyone%20from%20the%20Indian%20school%20of%20economists%20now%20and%20there%20is%20no%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20among%20the%20productive%20masses%20to%20understand%20this%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS-BJP%20government%20has%20close%20relationships%20with%20major%20industrialists.%20The%20Dwija%20industrialists%20have%20an%20ideological%20affinity%20with%20the%20political%20agenda%20of%20the%20RSS-BJP.%20The%20fact%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20there%20are%20no%20Dalits%2C%20Shudras%20and%20Adivasis%20among%20those%20major%20industrialists%20%E2%80%93%20except%20for%20the%20Shiv%20Nadar%20family.%20The%20presence%20of%20Gujarati%20Banias%20and%20Marwadis%20is%20so%20visible%20that%20no%20other%20caste%20can%20match%20them%20in%20manipulating%20Government%20resources%20to%20advance%20themselves.%20Ambani%2C%20Adani%2C%20Vedanta%2C%20Lakshmi%20Mittal%20and%20so%20on%20are%20known%20Bania%20industrialists.%20Infosys%2C%20%C2%A0the%20biggest%20software%20company%2C%20is%20run%20by%20a%20Brahmin%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20control%20over%20banks%2C%20it%20has%20written%20off%20lakhs%20of%20crores%20of%20loans%20given%20to%20big%20industrialists.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20the%20big%20businesses%20and%20big%20industrialists%20come%20from%20the%20Brahmin%2C%20Bania%2C%20Kayastha%2C%20Khatri%20and%20Kshatriya%20castes.%20There%20are%20hardly%20any%20Shudras%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20in%20that%20economy.%20The%20government%20investments%20in%20that%20economy%20do%20not%20benefit%20the%20productive%20Shudra%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%20government%20is%20against%20writing%20off%20small%20farm%20loans.%20Their%20economists%20keep%20arguing%20such%20a%20process%20will%20make%20the%20farmers%20lazy.%20But%20they%20never%20characterise%20industrialists%20as%20lazy%20or%20criminal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20huge%20amounts%20that%20go%20into%20such%20an%20industrial%20contract%20economy%20do%20not%20plough%20back%20into%20markets%20to%20upscale%20the%20GST%20returns%20to%20the%20state.%20Only%20some%20of%20it%20gets%20re-invested%2C%20some%20remains%20in%20the%20banks%20and%20some%20goes%20to%20foreign%20countries%20through%20hawala%20transactions%20and%20asset%20purchases.%20They%20live%20a%20life%20that%20could%20be%20called%20half-Indian%20with%20one%20foot%20in%20India%20and%20another%20foot%20in%20London%20or%20New%20York.%20The%20RSS-BJP%20project%20them%20as%20better%20nationalists%20than%20the%20Shudras%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20who%20always%20live%20in%20India%2C%20that%20too%20in%20villages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS-BJP%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20spending%20more%20and%20more%20budget%20on%20big%20infrastructure%20like%20massive%20highways%2C%20airports%20and%20seaports%20within%20India%20through%20this%20contract%20economy%2C%20in%20which%20there%20are%20massive%20profit%20ratios%2C%20completely%20goes%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20very%20same%20business%20castes.%20Even%20the%20rich%20agrarian%20Shudras%20have%20no%20share%20in%20that%20profit%20economy.%20Even%20the%20richest%20Shudra%20landed%20castes%20like%20Patels%2C%20Marathas%2C%20Jats%2C%20Reddys%2C%20Kammas%2C%20Lingayats%2C%20Vokkaligas%2C%20Mudaliyars%2C%20Nairs%20and%20so%20on%20do%20not%20get%20much%20share%20in%20this%20central%20contract%20economy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16172551%2Fpexels-matt-hardy-2624031.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16172551%2Fpexels-matt-hardy-2624031.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16172551%2Fpexels-matt-hardy-2624031-300x143.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16172551%2Fpexels-matt-hardy-2624031-1024x486.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-640801%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22570%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20highway.%20Photo%3A%20Matt%20Hardy%2FPexels%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20development%20that%20takes%20place%20in%20that%20economy%20is%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20a%20Brahmin-Bania%20Development%20Economy.%20It%20created%20an%20economic%20depression%20in%20the%20agrarian%20economy%20of%20India%2C%20because%20of%20under-growth%20in%20that%20sector%2C%20and%20also%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20enough%20investment.%20The%20Left%E2%80%99s%20economic%20analysis%20based%20on%20pure%20class%20methodology%20could%20never%20grasp%20this%20process.%20This%20caste%20blindness%20killed%20their%20ideology.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWherever%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20in%20the%20states%2C%20the%20welfare%20dose%20from%20the%20state%20budget%20to%20the%20agrarian%20and%20artisanal%20masses%20is%20very%20minimal.%20In%20the%20current%20elections%20to%20five%20state%20assemblies%20%E2%80%94%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Mizoram%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20package%20offered%20in%20the%20manifesto%20vis-a-vis%20the%20Congress%20and%20regional%20parties%20is%20the%20lowest.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20as%20against%20the%20BRS%20(regional%20party)%20welfare%20package%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20offered%20a%20far%20better%20agrarian%20welfare%20package.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20national%20party%20offered%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20acre%20investment%20and%20Rs%2012%2C000%20per%20person%20to%20agriculture%20labourers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20promises%20of%20old%20age%20pension%20too%2C%20and%20subsidised%20gas%20cylinders.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20now%20promising%20to%20write%20off%202%20lakh%20agriculture%20loans%20to%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20very%20seriously%20opposed.%20Yet%2C%20it%20has%20been%20consistently%20writing%20off%20bank%20loans%20of%20Dwija%20industrialists%20on%20a%20massive%20scale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20money%20pumped%20into%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20agrarian%20masses%20will%20be%20ploughed%20back%20into%20the%20rural%20markets%20within%20a%20month%20or%20two%2C%20and%20thereby%20into%20the%20GST%20income%20of%20the%20state.%20What%20is%20the%20BJP%20offering%20in%20Telangana%3F%20One%20cow%20per%20family%20and%20scrapping%20the%204%25%20reservation%20available%20for%20Muslims.%20Why%20does%20the%20RSS-BJP%20not%20want%20to%20send%20the%20budget%20money%20into%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20Shudra%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adiavasi%20people%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20but%20pump%20it%20into%20the%20rich%20industrialists%E2%80%99%20accounts%3F%20What%20is%20the%20opinion%20of%20an%20OBC%20Prime%20Minister%20about%20agrarian%20welfare%3F%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20hatred%20for%20agrarian%20producers%20is%20in%20tune%20with%20what%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Frevdi-culture-freebies-india-development-pm-modi-bundelkhand-expressway-launch-1976364-2022-07-16%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Erevdi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20culture%20(culture%20of%20freebies)%2C%20terming%20it%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%20Whose%20development%20is%20he%20so%20concerned%20about%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20against%20this%20view%20about%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20that%20are%20meant%20for%20the%20agrarian%20producers%2C%20Modi%20quite%20openly%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20was%20not%20among%20those%20who%20feared%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fnot-afraid-of-being-seen-with-industrialists-says-narendra-modi-398011.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estand%20beside%20industrialists%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20never%20stood%20among%20the%20farmers%20and%20agrarian%20labour.%20Development%20for%20Modi%20is%20Brahmin-Bania%20development.%20Unlike%20Modi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20Brahmin%2C%20goes%20and%20stands%20by%20labouring%20men%20and%20women%20in%20the%20fields.%20But%20the%20OBC%20prime%20minister%20never%20visits%20an%20agrarian%20field%20and%20stands%20with%20them.%20This%20approach%20of%20despising%20agriculture%20and%20the%20agrarian%20masses%20is%20learnt%20from%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Shudra%20development%20model%20improves%20rural%20life.%20When%20the%20state%20spends%20money%20from%20its%20budget%20on%20it%2C%20there%20is%20all-round%20development.%20This%20was%20witnessed%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20late%201960s%2C%20when%20the%20DMK%20came%20to%20power%20%E2%80%93%20it%20spent%20money%20on%20food%20for%20school%20children%2C%20books%2C%20and%20improving%20school%20infrastructure.%20The%20rural%20Tamil%20medium%20schools%20were%20meant%20for%20the%20Shudra%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20agrarian%20masses%2C%20whereas%20the%20Dwijas%20were%20sending%20their%20children%20to%20private%20English%20medium%20schools.%20Now%2C%20the%20spending%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20welfare%20for%20the%20rural%20masses%20is%20massive%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20transferring%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20money%20to%20the%20mothers%20of%20school%20and%20college-going%20children%2C%20spending%20money%20on%20improving%20the%20school%20infrastructure%20by%20stopping%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20so-called%20Singapore-like%20capital%20city%20in%20Amaravati%20has%20provided%20a%20new%20impetus%20to%20the%20Shudra%20Development%20Model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20interaction%20with%20agrarian%20masses%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20in%20the%20villages%2C%20in%20the%20roadside%20tea%20shops%2C%20he%20pushed%20a%20reluctant%20Congress%20to%20adopt%20the%20Shudra%20Development%20Model%20in%20the%20states%20that%20are%20going%20to%20election.%20They%20have%20done%20that%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20have%20promised%20to%20do%20so%20in%20Telangana.%20Since%20the%20Congress%2C%20an%20experienced%20national%20party%2C%20is%20going%20in%20this%20direction%2C%20there%20is%20certainly%20some%20hope.%20The%20Southern%20states%20are%20now%20moving%20in%20this%20new%20direction%20and%20a%20national%20party%20has%20come%20around%20to%20support%20the%20SDM%20as%20against%20the%20BBDM%2C%20which%20it%20was%20earlier%20supporting%20to%20various%20degrees.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EKancha%20Ilaiah%20Shepherd%20is%20a%20political%20theorist%2C%20social%20activist%20and%20author.%20His%20latest%20book%20is%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Clash%20of%20Cultures%20(Productive%20Masses%20Vs%20Hindutva-Mullah%20Conflicting%20Ethics)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701000961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F28164328%2FKokan-Farmer-Sindhudurg-Goa-Nature-Green-2795521.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-bjp-economic-development-model-upper-castes-industrialists-bahujans-production%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20decades%2C%20Indian%20economists%20and%20politicians%20have%20completely%20ignored%20the%20agrarian%20classes%20but%20things%20are%20changing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-bjp-economic-development-model-upper-castes-industrialists-bahujans-production%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20collapse%3A%20Families%20face%20agonising%20wait%20after%20rescue%20delay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700999116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F174BE%2Fproduction%2F_131822459_chaudary.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67535957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20pray%20to%20God...%20please%20don't%20take%20this%20son%20away%20from%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20s