2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%20says%20that%20she%20moved%20to%20her%20comfort%20zone%20%E2%80%94%20her%20home%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20last%20month%20before%20appearing%20for%20the%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20want%20to%20get%20influenced%20by%20anyone.%20I%20restricted%20talking%20to%20other%20aspirants.%20I%20only%20talked%20to%20friends%20from%20medicine%2C%20my%20teachers%2C%20and%20family%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20period%2C%20I%20focussed%20on%20revising%20the%20old%20content%20instead%20of%20learning%20new%20topics.%20Also%2C%20I%20would%20give%20mock%20papers%20once%20every%20three%20days.%20I%20would%20dedicate%20one%20whole%20day%20to%20analysing%20the%20mock%20paper%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IAS%20officer%20says%20she%20did%20not%20give%20any%20fancy%20answers%20to%20the%20interviewers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20says%20she%20did%20not%20give%20any%20fancy%20answers%20to%20the%20interviewers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%20stressed%20that%20giving%20more%20mocks%20does%20not%20help%20if%20aspirants%20do%20not%20analyse%20them.%20%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20their%20purpose%20is%20to%20teach%20you%20from%20your%20mistakes.%20The%20whole%20exercise%20is%20futile%20if%20you%20do%20not%20analyse%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20craft%20a%20powerful%20essay%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUPSC%20examination%20tests%20not%20only%20the%20content%20of%20your%20essay%20but%20also%20your%20writing%20skills%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20ideas%2C%20and%20how%20aspirants%20weave%20it%20all%20together.%20Saloni%20says%20acing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F189965%2Fupsc-exam-ias-topper-tips-essay-paper-cse-mains-interview-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessay%20writing%20%3C%2Fa%3Edoes%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20strategy%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wondered%20what%20kind%20of%20writing%20engages%20me%20as%20a%20reader.%20I%20would%20read%20the%20editorial%20section%20of%20The%20Hindu%20and%20write%20down%20my%20inference%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20story.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20incorporated%20that%20same%20style%20in%20my%20answer%20writing.%20Your%20essay%20should%20be%20crisp%2C%20engaging%2C%20and%20backed%20by%20facts.%20You%20can%20also%20include%20flowcharts%20to%20make%20answers%20interesting%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20fancy%20answers%20in%20the%20interview%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333542%2Fupsc-cse-interview-round-tips-by-ias-officers-personality-test-toppers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20IAS%20officer%20%3C%2Fa%3Esays%20she%20did%20not%20give%20any%20fancy%20answers%20to%20the%20interviewers.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%20myself%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20an%20instance%20from%20her%20interview.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20state-level%20silver%20medalist%20in%20taekwondo.%20I%20remember%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20looked%20so%20fragile%20and%20that%20it%20did%20not%20look%20like%20I%20could%20practice%20taekwondo.%20I%20politely%20said%20that%20strength%20matters%20more%20than%20physical%20appearance.%20I%20was%20not%20like%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20my%20god%2C%20sir%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20willpower%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20too%20senior%3B%20they%20understand%20when%20you%20are%20not%20being%20yourself.%20They%20do%20not%20appreciate%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Saloni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Mandla%20District%20Collectorate%20Facebook%2C%20Saloni%20Sidana%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700747920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Saloni%20Sidana%20pursued%20civil%20services%20after%20completing%20her%20MBBS.%20She%20aced%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%2074th%20rank%20in%20her%20first%20attempt.%20Serving%20as%20Mandla's%20district%20collector%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20she%20recently%20went%20viral%20for%20spending%20only%20Rs%20500%20on%20her%20wedding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334751%2Fias-officer-saloni-sidana-shares-strategy-for-cracking-upsc-cse-in-first-attemptsaloni-sidana-upsc-cse-in-first-attempt-district-collector-mandla-madhya-pradesh-wedding%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhanush%20Biopic%20on%20Isaignani%20Ilaiyaraaja%3A%20The%20Real%20Story%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Musical%20Sage%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIlaiyaraaja%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298846%2Fponniyin-selvan-must-watch-mani-ratnam-movies-yuva-alaipayuthey-nayakan-indian-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprolific%20musicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20has%20seen.%20The%20composer%20has%20regaled%20millions%20with%20his%20tunes%20for%20over%20five%20decades.%20Fondly%20called%20Raaja%2C%20the%2080-year-old%20has%20fans%20across%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Pannaipuram%20village%20in%20Theni%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20he%20stormed%20into%20the%20music%20industry%20in%20the%2070s%2C%20and%20ruled%20the%20Tamil%20music%20industry%20for%20several%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20composed%20over%208%2C000%20songs%20in%201%2C000%20films%20and%20has%20enthralled%20audiences%20through%20his%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20conferred%20with%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20and%20five%20National%20Awards%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Isaignani%E2%80%99%20(the%20musical%20sage)%20and%20was%20conferred%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Maestro%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Royal%20Philharmonic%20Orchestra%2C%20London%2C%20being%20the%20first%20Asian%20composer%20to%20record%20a%20symphony%20with%20them%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20credited%20with%20changing%20the%20way%20music%20is%20made%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247945%2Fsp-balasubrahmanyam-spb-padma-vibhushan-award-2021-singer-music-world-record-roja-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Tamil%20films.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20composers%20to%20use%20Western%20classical%20music%20and%20arrangements%20in%20his%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Tamil%20cinema%2C%20he%20has%20also%20scored%20music%20for%20Telugu%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Malayalam%20and%20Hindi%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3ECheeni%20Kum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EPaa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20humble%20background%20and%20upbringing%20heavily%20influenced%20his%20musical%20journey%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20his%20music%20infused%20with%20elements%20of%20regular%2C%20everyday%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20biopic%20on%20the%20maestro%20is%20in%20the%20making%20and%20actor%20Dhanush%20will%20reportedly%20essay%20the%20role.%20According%20to%20the%20reports%2C%20the%20film%20will%20go%20on%20floors%20in%202024%20and%20be%20released%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilm%20trade%20analyst%20Manobala%20Vijayabalan%20confirmed%20the%20news%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fan-artiste-of-the-millennium-ilaiyaraaja-at-75%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98An%20Artiste%20of%20the%20Millennium%3A%20Ilaiyaraaja%20at%2075%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Karthikeyan%20Damodaran%20for%20The%20Wire%2C%20Published%20on%2010%20September%2C%202018%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmovies%2Fregional-cinema%2Fstory%2Fdhanush-to-play-isaignani-ilaiyaraaja-in-upcoming-biopic-2456654-2023-11-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Dhanush%20to%20play%20Isaignani%20Ilaiyaraaja%20in%20upcoming%20biopic%3F%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20on%201%20November%2C%202023%20Courtesy%20India%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700747511000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22orig